'''卢旺达共和国'''（{{lang-rw|Repubulika y'u Rwanda}}，{{lang-fr|République du Rwanda}}，{{lang-en|Republic of Rwanda}}，{{lang-sw|Jamhuri ya Rwanda}}），通称'''卢旺达'''，是[[中部非洲|中非]][[东部非洲|东部]][[主权国家|主权国家]]，坐落在[[赤道|赤道]]以南，与[[乌干达|乌干达]]、[[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]]、[[布隆迪|布隆迪]]和[[刚果民主共和国|刚果民主共和国]]接壤。卢旺达地处[[大湖地区|大湖地区]]，海拔较高，地理上以西部的山区和东部的[[热带草原|热带草原]]为主，全国各地分布有多个湖泊。该国属温带到亚热带气候，每年有两个雨季和两个旱季。

卢旺达的人口主要居住在农村地区，以年轻人为主，密度在非洲国家中位居前列。卢旺达人主要分为三个族群：[[胡图族|胡图族]]、[[图西族|图西族]]和[[特瓦族|特瓦族]]。其中特瓦族是该国生活在森林中的最早居民[[俾格米人|俾格米人]]的后代，而在胡图族和图西族的起源上学术界尚未有一致結論，一些学者认为他们是由以前的种族社会衍生，另一部分学者则认为他们分别是从不同的种族和部落迁移过来。[[基督教|基督教]]是该国第一大[[宗教|宗教]]，主要语言是[[卢旺达语|卢旺达语]]，与[[法语|法语]]和[[英语|英语]]並列為该国的官方语言。卢旺达实行[[总统制|总统制]]政府，现任总统是[[卢旺达爱国阵线|卢旺达爱国阵线]]的[[保罗·卡加梅|保罗·卡加梅]]，于2000年上任。与邻国相比，如今的卢旺达贪污腐败的程度较低，不过人权组织报告称该国的反对派团体受到压制、[[言论自由|言论自由]]也遭到恐吓和限制。该国自前殖民时期以来就一直由严格的行政级别进行管理，全国按2006年划定的边界分成五个[[卢旺达行政区划|省]]。此外，卢旺达的女性国会议员比例为世界最高。

卢旺达自[[石器时代|石器]]和[[铁器时代|铁器时代]]就有人口在此[[狩猎采集|狩猎采集]]，之后又有[[班图人|班图人]]迁入。这些人口起初聚集成[[氏族|氏族]]社会，之后形成王国。18世纪中期，[[卢旺达王国|卢旺达王国]]开始统治这片土地，图西族国王征服了其他民族，集中权力，后来还制定了反胡图族的政策。1884年，德国开始对[[德属东非|东非]]实行殖民统治，卢旺达也相应成为[[德国殖民地|德国殖民地]]，之后又在1916年[[第一次世界大战|一战]]期间成为[[比利时殖民地|比利时殖民地]]。这两个欧洲国家都是通过卢旺达国王来统治该国，并延续其亲图西族政策。1959年，胡图族起兵造反，屠杀了大量图西族人，最终在1962年建立了一个以胡图族人占主导地位的独立国家。1990年，图西族领导的卢旺达爱国阵线发起[[卢旺达内战|内战]]，随之而来的是1994年的[[卢旺达大屠杀|种族灭绝]]，估计受胡图族极端分子屠杀的图西族人與温和派胡图族人有50至100万。最终卢旺达爱国阵线取得了军事上的胜利，这场种族灭绝才相应中止。

卢旺达的[[经济|经济]]在1994年的大屠杀期间受到重创，不过此后得以复苏。国家经济主要依靠[[自给农业|自给农业]]，[[咖啡|咖啡]]和[[茶叶|茶叶]]是主要的出口经济作物。该国[[旅游业|旅游业]]增长迅速，如今已是占主导地位的外汇收入来源。卢旺达是仅有的两个能够安全看到[[山地大猩猩|山地大猩猩]]的国家之一，许多游客都愿意为获得大猩猩的追踪许可支付高价。音乐和舞蹈是该国文化的重要组成部分，特别是鼓乐和一种名为“{{lang|en|intore}}”的民族舞蹈。全国各地都有传统工艺品制作，其中包括一种名为“{{lang|en|imigongo}}”，使用[[牛粪|牛粪]]制作的独特艺术品。

== 历史 ==
[[File:Rwanda_Nyanza_Mwami_Palace.jpg|thumb]]的一幢再造的卢旺达国王宫殿。]]
{{main|卢旺达历史|德屬東非|盧安達-烏隆地}}
现代人类定居如今卢旺达所在地的日期可以追溯到[[末次冰期|末次冰期]]或是约公元前8000年的[[新石器时代|新石器时代]]，还可能是其后公元前约3000年的[[新石器亚雨期|漫长潮湿时期]]<ref name="Chrétien 2003">{{cite book | last = Chrétien | first = Jean-Pierre | year = 2003 | title = The Great Lakes of Africa: Two Thousand Years of History | location = Cambridge, Mass. | publisher = MIT Press | isbn = 978-1-890951-34-4 | accessdate = 2014-04-15 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=Ezo5PQAACAAJ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130610005001/http://books.google.com/books?id=Ezo5PQAACAAJ | archivedate = 2013-06-10 }}</ref>{{rp|44}}。考古发掘获得的证据表明，[[石器时代|石器时代]]后期就有稀疏的人口定居在此[[狩猎采集|狩猎采集]]，随后的[[铁器时代|铁器时代]]早期又有了更多定居者，他们制作有波纹[[陶器|陶器]]和铁制工具<ref name="Dorsey 1994">{{cite book | last = Dorsey | first = Learthen | year = 1994 | title = Historical Dictionary of Rwanda | url = https://archive.org/details/historicaldictio0000dors | location = Metuchen, N.J. | publisher = Scarecrow Press | isbn = 978-0-8108-2820-9 | page = [https://archive.org/details/historicaldictio0000dors/page/36 36]}}</ref><ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|45}}。这些早期居民正是如今生活在卢旺达的[[特瓦族|特瓦族]]以及仍然按狩猎采集方式生活的[[俾格米人|俾格米人]]原住民的祖先<ref name="Mamdani 2002">{{cite book | last = Mamdani | first = Mahmood | year = 2002 | title = When Victims Become Killers: Colonialism, Nativism, and the Genocide in Rwanda | location = Princeton, N.J. | publisher = Princeton University Press | isbn = 978-0-691-10280-1 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=QUEamxb89JcC | accessdate = 2014-04-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210217064045/https://books.google.com/books?id=QUEamxb89JcC | archivedate = 2021-02-17 }}</ref>{{rp|61}}。公元前700年到公元1500年间，一些[[班图人|班图人]]群体迁入卢旺达，毁林开荒种植农作物<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|58}}<ref name="Mamdani 2002" />{{rp|61}}。居住在森林中的特瓦族失去了大部分栖息地，于是迁往山坡地区<ref name="King 2007">{{cite book | last = King | first = David C. | year = 2007 | title = Rwanda (Cultures of the World) | location = New York, N.Y. | publisher = Benchmark Books | isbn = 978-0-7614-2333-1 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=1yLx1zSuh_QC | accessdate = 2014-04-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200930190813/https://books.google.com/books?id=1yLx1zSuh_QC | archivedate = 2020-09-30 }}</ref>{{rp|75}}。对于班图人迁入卢旺达的原因，[[历史学家|历史学家]]有多种不同看法，一种认为首批定居者是[[胡图族|胡图族]]，而[[图西族|图西族]]是之后从另一个种族群体迁移过来，这个种族群体有可能是[[库希特语族|库希特语族]]<ref name="Prunier 1995">{{cite book | last = Prunier | first = Gérard | year = 1995 | title = The Rwanda Crisis, 1959–1994: History of a Genocide | edition = 2nd | location = London | publisher = C. Hurst & Co. Publishers | accessdate = 2014-04-15 | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books/about/The_Rwanda_Crisis_1959_1994.html?id=6hwCdeYHZKcC | isbn = 978-1-85065-243-4 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140416180325/http://books.google.com.hk/books/about/The_Rwanda_Crisis_1959_1994.html?id=6hwCdeYHZKcC | archivedate = 2014-04-16 }}</ref>{{rp|16}}。另一种理论认为迁移是以缓慢的步调持续进行，新进的族群融入了原有群体，而非将其征服<ref name="Mamdani 2002" />{{rp|58, 61}}。根据第二种理论，胡图族和图西族之后出现的区别就属于等级而非种族性的差别<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|69}}<ref name="Shyaka">{{cite web | last = Shyaka | first = Anastase | title = The Rwandan Conflict: Origin, Development, Exit Strategies | publisher = National Unity and Reconciliation Commission, Republic of Rwanda | archivedate = 2013-12-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131229111858/http://repositories.lib.utexas.edu/bitstream/handle/2152/4746/3833.pdf?sequence=1 | url = http://repositories.lib.utexas.edu/bitstream/handle/2152/4746/3833.pdf?sequence=1 | accessdate = 2014-04-15 | page = 10-11 }}</ref>。

[[氏族|氏族]]（当地人称“{{lang|rw|ubwoko}}”）是这片土地上最早形成的社会组织形式<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|88}}。大湖地区存在多个氏族，其中在如今卢旺达境内生活的就有约20个<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|88-89}}。氏族并不仅限于家谱谱系或地域区分，其中大部分都包括有胡图族、图西族和特瓦族人<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|88-89}}。氏族从15世纪开始聚结成王国<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|141}}，到1700年时，如今的卢旺达境内一共有8个王国<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|482}}。其中由图西族“{{lang|en|Nyiginya}}”氏族统治的卢旺达王国从18世纪中期开始逐渐壮大<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|160}}，到19世纪时已在国王[[基加利四世|基加利四世]]的统治下达到巅峰。基加利四世征服了多个小国，将自己的王国向西面和北面延伸<ref name="Mamdani 2002" />{{rp|69}}<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|160}}，还发起了多项行政改革，例如在名为“{{lang|en|ubuhake}}”的社会秩序下，图西族可以放弃黄牛来获得特权地位，换取经济和个人服务<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|13-14}}，还有一种名为“{{lang|en|uburetwa}}”的[[徭役|徭役]]制度，强迫胡图族为图西族酋长工作<ref name="Mamdani 2002" />{{rp|69}}。基加利四世的改革导致胡图族和图西族之间的裂缝不断加大<ref name="Mamdani 2002" />{{rp|69}}。特瓦族的生活则相对来说比组建王国前要好，一些人成为宫廷中的舞者<ref name="King 2007" />{{rp|75}}，但其人数则在不断下降<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|6}}。
[[File:Flag_of_Rwanda_(1962-2001).svg|thumb]]
1884年，[[柏林西非会议|柏林西非会议]]将这片领地作为[[德属东非|德属东非]]的一部分划归[[德意志帝国|德意志帝国]]，标志着卢旺达殖民时代的开始。1894年，[[古斯塔夫·阿道夫·冯·格岑|古斯塔夫·阿道夫·冯·格岑]]（{{lang|de|Gustav Adolf von Götzen}}）成为首位对该国进行过大规模探索的欧洲探险家，他从东南方向越过基伍湖并得到国王的接见<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|217}}<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|9}}。德国人接下来没有大幅改变卢旺达王国的社会结构，而是通过支持国王并把权力下放给各地方酋长来产生影响<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|25}}。[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]後，德國戰敗，[[比利时殖民地|比利时]]获得了卢旺达和布隆迪地区的控制权，开始对这里实行更加直接的殖民统治<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|260}}。在比利时的统治下，权力结构有所简化并且更加集中<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|270}}，还新增了涉及[[教育|教育]]、卫生、公共建设和农业监查之类的大型项目，其中包括引入新的农作物和改良的农业技术，以求尽量减少出现饥荒的可能性<ref name="Chrétien 2003" />{{rp|276-277}}。德国和比利时的殖民统治都令图西族的霸权有所增强，将图西族和胡图族视为不同的[[人种|种族]]<ref name="Appiah-Gates-2010">{{cite book | last1 = Appiah | first1 = Anthony | last2 = Gates | first2 = Henry Louis | year = 2010 | title = Encyclopedia of Africa, Volume 1 | edition = illustrated | location = Oxford | publisher = Oxford University Press | url = http://books.google.com/?id=A0XNvklcqbwC | isbn = 978-0-19-533770-9 | accessdate = 2014-04-15 | page = 450}}</ref>。1935年，比利时引入了新的身份证制度，其上会标明证主是图西族、胡图族、特瓦族或是入籍人士。以前那些特别富裕的胡图族人都还是有着在名誉上成为图西族的可能性，但新的身份证制度则让不同阶层之间不可能再存在任何的变动<ref name="Gourevitch-2000">{{cite book | last = Gourevitch | first = Philip | year = 2000 | title = We Wish To Inform You That Tomorrow We Will Be Killed With Our Families | edition = Reprint | location = London; New York, N.Y. | publisher = Picador | isbn = 978-0-330-37120-9 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=8OiMfpTiApQC | accessdate = 2014-04-15}}</ref>{{rp|56-57}}。
[[File:Juvénal_Habyarimana_(1980).jpg|thumb]]]]
[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]结束后，[[比利时|比利时]]继续治理成为[[联合国托管领土|联合国托管领土]]的卢旺达，负责监督其[[非洲非殖民化|独立进程]]<ref name="United Nations (II)">{{cite web | author = United Nations (II) | title = International Trusteeship System | archivedate = 2014-04-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140412173643/http://www.un.org/en/decolonization/its.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.un.org/en/decolonization/its.shtml | accessdate = 2014-04-15 }}</ref><ref name="United Nations (III)">{{cite web | author = United Nations (III) | title = Trust and Non-Self-Governing Territories (1945–1999) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140412164540/http://www.un.org/en/decolonization/nonselfgov.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.un.org/en/decolonization/nonselfgov.shtml | accessdate = 2014-04-15 | archivedate = 2014-04-12 }}</ref>。主张早日独立的图西族和胡图族解放运动之间的紧张局势不断升级，最终在1959年的[[卢旺达革命|卢旺达革命]]中达到高潮：胡图族激进分子开始屠杀图西族，迫使超过10万图西族人向周边国家寻求避难<ref name="Gourevitch-2000" />{{rp|58-59}}<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|51}}。1961年，改站在胡图族一方的比利时人在卢旺达举行了一次全民公投，公投结果废除了[[君主制|君主制]]。1962年，卢旺达与布隆迪分离并获得独立<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|53}}。随之而来的则是暴力的循环，流亡邻国的图西族向国内发起进攻，胡图族则以对国内图西族展开大规模屠杀和镇压加以报复<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|56}}。1973年，[[朱韦纳尔·哈比亚利马纳|朱韦纳尔·哈比亚利马纳]]通过[[军事政变|军事政变]]上台。亲胡图族的歧视仍在继续，但国家经济状况已有所改善，针对图西族的暴力活动也相应减少<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|74-76}}。特瓦族仍然是该国的边缘化群体，到1990年时，他们几乎已完全被政府从树林中驱逐出去，许多人都沦为乞丐<ref name="UNPO-2008">{{cite web | author = Unrepresented Nations and Peoples Organization (UNPO) | date = 2008-03-25 | title = Batwa | url = http://www.unpo.org/members/7861 | accessdate = 2014-04-15 | archivedate = 2014-04-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140402134444/http://unpo.org/members/7861 }}</ref>。同时，卢旺达的人口已从1934年的160万增加到1989年的710万，导致人们开始争夺土地<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|4}}。
1990年，大部分成员是图西族难民的反叛组织卢旺达爱国阵线从该国北部入侵，引发了[[卢旺达内战|卢旺达内战]]<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|93}}，任何一方都无法在战争中取得决定性的优势<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|135-136}}，但到了1992年，哈比亚利马纳的权威已遭削弱，大规模的示威活动迫使他和国内反对派结盟，并于1993年和卢旺达爱国阵线签订了《[[阿鲁沙协定|阿鲁沙协定]]》<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|190-191}}。1994年4月6日，朱韦纳尔·哈比亚利马纳和[[西普里安·恩塔里亚米拉|西普里安·恩塔里亚米拉]]乘坐的专机在基加利机场附近被[[导弹|导弹]][[朱韦纳尔·哈比亚利马纳和西普里安·恩塔里亚米拉遇刺案|击落]]，两人当场死亡，内战双方也随即重燃战火<ref name="BBC News (III)-2010">{{cite news | author = BBC News (III) | date = 2010-01-12 | title = Hutus 'killed Rwanda President Juvenal Habyarimana' | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/8453832.stm | accessdate = 2014-04-15 | archivedate = 2013-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130601115647/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/8453832.stm | deadurl = no }}</ref>。这起击落事件也成为几个小时后爆发的[[卢旺达种族灭绝|卢旺达种族灭绝]]的导火索，在短短的约100天时间里，临时政府通过周密计划，杀害了50至100万<ref name=Henley-2007>{{cite news | last = Henley | first = Jon | date = 2007-10-31 | title = Scar tissue | work = The Guardian | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140224022044/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2007/oct/31/rwanda.theatre | deadurl = no | url = http://www.theguardian.com/world/2007/oct/31/rwanda.theatre | accessdate = 2014-04-15 | location = London | archivedate = 2014-02-24 }}</ref>图西族人和政治上较为温和的胡图族人<ref name="Dallaire-2005">{{cite book | last = Dallaire | first = Roméo | year = 2005 | title = Shake Hands with the Devil: The Failure of Humanity in Rwanda | location = London | publisher = Arrow | isbn = 978-0-09-947893-5 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=Ja2hQgAACAAJ | accessdate = 2014-04-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201028001304/https://books.google.com/books?id=Ja2hQgAACAAJ | archivedate = 2020-10-28 }}</ref>{{rp|386}}，此外还有许多不是直接目标的特瓦族人被杀<ref name="UNPO-2008" />。图西族领导的卢旺达爱国阵线重新启动了攻势，有条不紊地夺取国家的控制权，到7月中旬时已控制全国<ref name="Dallaire-2005" />{{rp|299}}。国际社会对这场种族灭绝的反应有限，[[联合国卢旺达援助团|联合国维和部队]]已是不堪重负，各个大国又不愿施以援手<ref name="Dallaire-2005" />{{rp|364}}。等到卢旺达爱国阵线占领全国时，已有约200万胡图族人因担心受到报复而[[大湖地区难民危机|逃往邻国]]，其中又以[[扎伊尔|扎伊尔]]最多<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|312}}。此外，由卢旺达爱国阵线领导的军队还是[[第一次刚果战争|第一]]和[[第二次刚果战争|第二次刚果战争]]中的主要交战方之一<ref name="BBC News (VI)-2010">{{cite news | author = BBC News (VI) | date = 2010-08-27 | title = Q&A: DR Congo conflict | archivedate = 2014-03-11 | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-11108589 | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140311044311/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-11108589 }}</ref>。之后，卢旺达开始进入一段和解和公正时期，[[卢旺达问题国际刑事法庭|卢旺达问题国际刑事法庭]]和名为“{{lang|en|Gacaca}}”的传统乡村法院系统相继建立。进入21世纪后，卢旺达的经济、游客人数以及[[人类发展指数|人类发展指数]]都得到迅猛增长<ref name="UNDP (III)-2010">{{cite web | author = United Nations Development Programme (UNDP) (III) | year = 2010 | title = Human Development Index Trends, 1980–2010 | url = http://hdr.undp.org/en/media/HDR_2010_EN_Table2.pdf | accessdate = 2013-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131113093156/http://hdr.undp.org/en/media/HDR_2010_EN_Table2.pdf | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-11-13 }}</ref><ref name="RDB (I)-2009">{{cite web | author = Rwanda Development Board (RDB) (I) | date = 2009-01-06 | title = Tourism and Conservation Performance in 2008 | archivedate = 2012-05-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120511233622/http://www.rwandatourism.com/tourism_performance_2008.htm | url = http://www.rwandatourism.com/tourism_performance_2008.htm | accessdate = 2012-05-11 }}</ref>，贫困率从2006年的57%下降到2011年的45%<ref name="National Institute of Statistics of Rwanda-2012">{{cite web | author = National Institute of Statistics of Rwanda | date = 2012-02 | title = The third Integrated Household Living Conditions Survey (EICV 3) – Main indicators Report | archivedate = 2013-11-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131113204052/http://www.statistics.gov.rw/publications/third-integrated-household-living-conditions-survey-eicv-3-main-indicators-report | url = http://www.statistics.gov.rw/publications/third-integrated-household-living-conditions-survey-eicv-3-main-indicators-report | accessdate = 2014-04-16 }}</ref>，[[预期寿命|预期寿命]]也从2000年的46.6岁<ref>{{cite web |author=United Nations Development Programme (UNDP) (V) |year=2013 |title=Human Development Report 2013: Rwanda |url=http://hdr.undp.org/sites/default/files/Country-Profiles/RWA.pdf |accessdate=2015-08-31 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160213002248/http://hdr.undp.org/sites/default/files/Country-Profiles/RWA.pdf |archivedate=2016-02-13 }}</ref>增长到2015年的59.7岁<ref>{{cite web |author=Central Intelligence Agency (CIA) (I) |work=[[The_World_Factbook|The World Factbook]] |title=Rwanda |authorlink=CIA |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/rw.html |accessdate=2015-11-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107033348/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/rw.html |archivedate=2015-11-07 }}</ref>。

== 政治和政府 ==
[[File:Paul_Kagame_New_York_2010.jpg|thumb]]]]
[[卢旺达总统|卢旺达总统]]是[[国家元首|国家元首]]<ref name="CJCR-2003">{{cite web | author = Commission Juridique Et Constitutionnelle Du Rwanda (CJCR) | date = 2003-05-26 | title = Constitution of the Republic of Rwanda | url = http://www.cjcr.gov.rw/eng/constitution_eng.doc | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090325123325/http://www.cjcr.gov.rw/eng/constitution_eng.doc | archivedate = 2009-03-25 | accessdate = 2012-02-16 }}</ref>{{rp|98}}，拥有涉及多个范围的权力，其中包括与内阁一起制定政策<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|117}}、行使赦免权<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|111}}，指挥[[卢旺达国防军|武装部队]]<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|110}}，谈判和缔结条约<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|189}}，签署总统令<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|112}}，以及[[宣战|宣战]]或是宣布进入紧急状态<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|110}}，还可以任命[[卢旺达总理|总理]]和所有内阁成员<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|116}}。总统任期七年，由民众投票选举产生<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|100-101}}，现任总统是[[保罗·卡加梅|保罗·卡加梅]]，于2000年前任总统[[巴斯德·比齐蒙古|巴斯德·比齐蒙古]]辞职后开始就职，之后又在2003年、[[2010年卢旺达总统选举|2010年]]与2017年的总统选举中获胜<ref name="Lacey-2003">{{cite news | last = Lacey | first = Marc | date = 2003-08-26 | title = Rwandan President Declares Election Victory | work = New York Times | archivedate = 2013-11-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111064327/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/08/26/world/rwandan-president-declares-election-victory.html | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2003/08/26/world/rwandan-president-declares-election-victory.html | accessdate = 2014-04-16 }}</ref><ref name="BBC News (IV)-2010">{{cite news | author = BBC News (IV) | date = 2010-08-11 | title = Rwanda President Kagame wins election with 93% of vote | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-10935892 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120425041020/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-10935892 | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-04-25 }}</ref>。不过，有人权组织批评这些选举所代表的是政治压迫和对言论自由镇压的增长<ref name="HRW-2010">{{cite news | author = Human Rights Watch (HRW) | date = 2010-08-02 | title = Rwanda: Silencing Dissent Ahead of Elections | quote = marked by increasing political repression and a crackdown on free speech | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archivedate = 2014-03-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309101006/http://www.hrw.org/news/2010/08/02/rwanda-attacks-freedom-expression-freedom-association-and-freedom-assembly-run-presi | url = http://www.hrw.org/news/2010/08/02/rwanda-attacks-freedom-expression-freedom-association-and-freedom-assembly-run-presi }}</ref>。

卢旺达的现行[[卢旺达宪法|宪法]]于2003年经全民公投通过，取代了自1994年开始生效的过渡时期宪法<ref name="Media High Council">{{cite web | author = Media High Council, Republic of Rwanda | title = Constitution of June 2003 | url = http://www.mhc.gov.rw/services/the-constitution-of-the-republic-of-rwanda-of-june-2003.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120615053421/http://www.mhc.gov.rw/services/the-constitution-of-the-republic-of-rwanda-of-june-2003.html | accessdate = 2012-06-15 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-06-15 }}</ref>。宪法规定政府实行[[多党制|多党制]]，政治运作基于民主和选举进行<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|52}}。在政党的运作形式方面，第54条规定：“禁止根据种族、族裔群体、部落、氏族、地区、性别、宗教信仰等任何可能导致歧视的因素来组建政治组织”<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|54}}。政府还颁布了将种族灭绝思想入罪的法律，包括像恐吓、诽谤性言论、[[否认种族灭绝|否认种族灭绝]]以及嘲笑受害人的行为都可以归入刑事犯罪<ref name=National>{{cite web |author=National Commission for the Fight against Genocide, Republic of Rwanda |date=2008-10-15 |title=Law No 18/2008 of 23/07/2008 Relating to the Punishment of the Crime of Genocide Ideology |page=1 |archivedate=2013-11-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131108175534/http://www.cnlg.gov.rw/sites/cnlg.gov.rw/files/genocide_laws/Law%20relating%20to%20the%20punishment%20of%20the%20crime%20of%20genocide%20ideology.doc |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.cnlg.gov.rw/sites/cnlg.gov.rw/files/genocide_laws/Law%20relating%20to%20the%20punishment%20of%20the%20crime%20of%20genocide%20ideology.doc |accessdate=2014-04-16 }}</ref>。根据[[人权观察|人权观察]]的报告，这些法律令卢旺达成为了实际上的[[一党制|一党制]]国家，“在防止又一次种族灭绝的幌子下，政府显然对最基本形式的不同政见也无法容忍”<ref name="Roth-2009">{{cite web | last = Roth | first = Kenneth | date = 2009-04-11 | title = The power of horror in Rwanda | publisher = Human Rights Watch | url = http://www.hrw.org/news/2009/04/11/power-horror-rwanda | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320191137/http://www.hrw.org/news/2009/04/11/power-horror-rwanda | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archivedate = 2014-03-20 | quote = under the guise of preventing another genocide, the government displays a marked intolerance of the most basic forms of dissent. }}</ref>。[[国际特赦组织|国际特赦组织]]也持负面看法，称这些将种族灭绝思想入罪法律的实际效果就是消除异议，包括针对执政党卢旺达爱国阵线的批评，以及公正处理卢旺达爱国阵线所犯下的战争罪行的要求<ref name="Amnesty International-2010">{{cite web | author = Amnesty International | year = 2012 | title = Human Rights in Republic of Rwanda | url = http://www.amnesty.org/en/region/rwanda/report-2010 | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | quote = silence dissent, including criticisms of the ruling RPF party and demands for justice for RPF war crimes. | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140422191325/http://www.amnesty.org/en/region/rwanda/report-2010 | archivedate = 2014-04-22 }}</ref><ref name="Amnesty International-2012">{{cite web | author = Amnesty International | year = 2012 | title = Human Rights in Republic of Rwanda | url = http://www.amnesty.org/en/region/rwanda/report-2012 | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002043850/http://www.amnesty.org/en/region/rwanda/report-2012 | archivedate = 2013-10-02 }}</ref>。

卢旺达议会实行[[两院制|两院制]]，宪法赋予议会立法权，并且可以监督总统和内阁的运作<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|62}}。其中的[[下议院|下议院]]是卢旺达众议院，拥有80位议员，任期5年。所有议席中有24个保留给女性，这些女性议员都是通过地方政府官员组成的联合大会选举产生；另外还有三个议席为青少年和残疾人保留，剩下的53个席位则按[[比例代表制|比例代表制]]经[[普通选举|普通选举]]产生<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|76}}。2008年的议会选举共计产生了45位女性众议员，卢旺达也因此成为全世界唯一一个女性在全国性议会中占据多数的国家<ref name="UNIFEM-2008">{{cite news | author = United Nations Development Fund for Women (UNIFEM) | date = 2008-09-22 | title = Rwandan Women Secure 56% of Parliamentary Seats in Historic Election Result | url = http://www.unifem.org/news_events/story_detail882c.html | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-12-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131213053702/http://www.unifem.org/news_events/story_detail882c.html }}</ref>。卢旺达参议院是两院中的[[上议院|上议院]]，通过各种团体选出，至少30%的参议员必须是女性，参议员的任期为八年<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|82}}。

[[File:RwandaParliament.jpg|thumb]]
卢旺达的法律制度很大程度上基于[[德国法系|德国]]与[[比利时法系|比利时]][[欧陆法系|大陆法系]]和[[习惯法|习惯法]]<ref name="CIA (I)">{{cite web | author = Central Intelligence Agency (CIA) (I) | work = The World Factbook | title = Rwanda | url = https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/rw.html | accessdate = 2012-04-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120302152119/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/rw.html | archivedate = 2012-03-02 }}</ref>。司法部门与行政部门独立<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|140}}，不过[[最高法院|最高法院]]法官的指派是由总统和参议院进行<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|148}}。[[人权观察|人权观察]]曾称赞卢旺达政府在实现司法公正上做出了包括[[废除死刑|废除死刑]]在内的努力<ref name="HRW-Wells-2008-chapterI-Summary">{{cite book | author1 = Human Rights Watch (HRW) | author2 = Wells, Sarah | year = 2008 | title = Law and reality: progress in judicial reform in Rwanda | isbn = 978-1-56432-366-8 | url = http://www.hrw.org/node/62098 | chapterurl = http://www.hrw.org/node/62097/section/2 | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | chapter = I. Summary | page = 2 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320221926/http://www.hrw.org/node/62097/section/2 | archivedate = 2014-03-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，但也指称政府成员对司法系统存在不当干涉，例如出于政治动机来任命法官，以及向法官施压，令其做出某些特定裁决等<ref name="HRW-Wells-2008-chapterVIII-Independence of the Judiciary">{{cite book | author1 = Human Rights Watch (HRW) | author2 = Wells, Sarah | year = 2008 | title = Law and reality: progress in judicial reform in Rwanda | isbn = 978-1-56432-366-8 | page = 9 | url = http://www.hrw.org/node/62098 | chapterurl = http://www.hrw.org/node/62097/section/9 | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | chapter = VIII. Independence of the Judiciary | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320222010/http://www.hrw.org/node/62097/section/9 | archivedate = 2014-03-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。宪法中规定有两种类型的法院：普通法院和专用法院<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|143}}。卢旺达的最高法院、高等法院和区域性法院都属普通法院，专用法院则包括[[军事法庭|军事法庭]]和传统的“{{lang|en|Gacaca}}”法院，其中恢复“{{lang|en|Gacaca}}”法院是为了加快对种族灭绝犯罪嫌疑人的审判<ref name="Walker-2004-03">{{cite news | last = Walker | first = Robert | date = 2004-03-30 | title = Rwanda still searching for justice | archivedate = 2013-12-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131226012239/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/3557753.stm | deadurl = no | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/3557753.stm | work = BBC News | accessdate = 2014-04-16 }}</ref>。

与其他大部分非洲国家相比，卢旺达的腐败程度较为轻微。2010年，[[透明国际|透明国际]]将其评为[[撒哈拉以南非洲|撒哈拉以南非洲]]47个国家中第8清廉的国家，在全世界的178个国家中则名列第66位<ref name="Transparency International-2010">{{cite web | author = Transparency International | year = 2010 | title = Corruption Perceptions Index 2010 Results | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140412212208/http://www.transparency.org/cpi2010/results | archivedate = 2014-04-12 | url = http://www.transparency.org/cpi2010/results | accessdate = 2014-04-16 }}</ref>。宪法规定[[申诉专员|申诉专员]]的主要职责就是预防和打击腐败<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|182}}<ref name="Office of the Ombudsman">{{cite web | author = Office of the Ombudsman, Republic of Rwanda | title = Office of the Ombudsman | url = http://www.ombudsman.gov.rw/ | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archivedate = 2014-03-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140326102803/http://www.ombudsman.gov.rw/ }}</ref>。宪法还规定，包括总统在内的公职人员必须向申诉专员和公众申报自己拥有的财富，否则将受到停职<ref name="Asiimwe-2011">{{cite news | last = Asiimwe | first = Bosco R | date = 2011-09-28 | title = Gov't to sanction officials who failed to declare wealth | work = The New Times | location = Kigali | url = http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14762&a=45647 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140416070950/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14762&a=45647 | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archivedate = 2014-04-16 }}</ref>。

卢旺达爱国阵线自1994年以来就一直是该国的主导[[政党|政党]]，在全国大选中保持着对总统和议会位置的控制权，党派的得票率始终在70%以上。一般认为卢旺达爱国阵线属图西族占主导地位的党派，但全国各地都因能确保持续的和平、稳定和经济增长而对其表示支持<ref name="Clark-2010">{{cite news | last = Clark | first = Phil | date = 2010-08-05 | title = Rwanda: Kagame's power struggle | work = The Guardian | archivedate = 2014-03-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320235655/http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/libertycentral/2010/aug/05/rwanda-kagames-power-struggle | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | location = London | url = http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/libertycentral/2010/aug/05/rwanda-kagames-power-struggle }}</ref>。不过，包括国际特赦组织和[[自由之家|自由之家]]在内的人权组织声称，卢旺达政府会通过只允许对政府态度友好政党的候选人参加选举、镇压示威活动以及逮捕反对派领导人和记者来压制反对派组织的自由<ref name="Amnesty International-2010" /><ref name="Freedom House-2011">{{cite web | author = Freedom House | year = 2011 | title = Freedom in the World: Rwanda | url = http://www.freedomhouse.org/report/freedom-world/2011/rwanda#.U0408FWSyqk | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320185936/http://www.freedomhouse.org/report/freedom-world/2011/rwanda#.U0408FWSyqk | archivedate = 2014-03-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

卢旺达是[[联合国|联合国]]<ref name="United Nations (I)">{{cite web | author = United Nations (I) | title = United Nations Member States | url = http://www.un.org/en/members/index.shtml | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archivedate = 2014-04-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140412154940/http://www.un.org/en/members/index.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>、[[非洲联盟|非洲联盟]]、[[法语圈国际组织|法语圈国际组织]]<ref name="Francophonie">{{cite web | author = Francophonie | title = Welcome to the International Organisation of La Francophonie's official website | url = http://www.francophonie.org/Welcome-to-the-International.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140401162352/http://www.francophonie.org/Welcome-to-the-International.html | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archivedate = 2014-04-01 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>、[[东非共同体|东非共同体]]<ref name="Grainger-2007">{{cite news | last = Grainger | first = Sarah | date = 2007-06-18 | title = East Africa trade bloc expanded | work = BBC News | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/6762615.stm | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130414000116/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/6762615.stm | archivedate = 2013-04-14 }}</ref>和[[英联邦|英联邦]]的成员国<ref name="Fletcher-2009">{{cite news | last = Fletcher | first = Pascal | date = 2009-11-30 | title = Rwanda accepted into Commonwealth only 15 years after genocide | work = The Scotsman | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130615101302/http://www.scotsman.com/news/uk/rwanda-accepted-into-commonwealth-only-15-years-after-genocide-1-770271 | archivedate = 2013-06-15 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | location = Edinburgh | url = http://www.scotsman.com/news/uk/rwanda-accepted-into-commonwealth-only-15-years-after-genocide-1-770271 }}</ref>。该国在哈比亚利马纳执政的多年时间里一直保持着和[[法国|法国]]以及前宗主国比利时的密切联系<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|89}}。但自卢旺达爱国阵线掌权后，卢旺达开始寻求与邻近的东非国家以及英语世界国家建立更为密切的关系。2006至2010年，该国与法国之间的外交关系陷入僵局，因为有一位法国法官对卢旺达官员提出了起诉<ref name="Department of State (III)-2012">{{cite web | author = Department of State (III) | year = 2012 | title = Background Note: Rwanda | work = Background Notes | url = http://www.state.gov/r/pa/ei/bgn/2861.htm | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140412174137/http://www.state.gov/r/pa/ei/bgn/2861.htm | archivedate = 2014-04-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。同时卢旺达还因参与了[[第一次刚果战争|第一]]和[[第二次刚果战争|第二次刚果战争]]导致与[[刚果民主共和国|刚果民主共和国]]的关系紧张<ref name="BBC News (VI)-2010" />，刚果军方声称曾受到卢旺达部队的攻击，而卢旺达则指责刚果政府未能有效压制[[南基伍省|南]]、[[北基伍省|北基伍省]]的胡图族反政府武装<ref name="USA Today-2008">{{cite news | author = USA Today | date = 2008-10-29 | title = Congolese army claims attack by Rwandan troops | archivedate = 2012-11-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121104070524/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/world/2008-10-29-congo-fighting_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/world/2008-10-29-congo-fighting_N.htm | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="Al Jazeera-2007">{{cite news | author = Al Jazeera | date = 2007-09-20 | title = Rwanda blames DR Congo for violence | url = http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2007/09/2008525143037439552.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320233549/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2007/09/2008525143037439552.html | archivedate = 2014-03-20 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-04-16 }}</ref>。卢旺达与[[乌干达|乌干达]]的关系自进入21世纪以来也很紧张，因为两国曾在第二次刚果战争期间支持相互对立的叛乱集团，两国军队还曾在1999年发生过冲突<ref name="Heuler-2011">{{cite news | last = Heuler | first = Hilary | date = 2011-12-12 | title = Uganda, Rwanda Move to Mend Troubled Relations | work = Voice of America News | archivedate = 2014-03-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140321025547/http://www.voanews.com/content/uganda-and-rwanda-move-to-mend-troubled-relations-135437603/149440.html | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | url = http://www.voanews.com/content/uganda-and-rwanda-move-to-mend-troubled-relations-135437603/149440.html }}</ref>。不过到了2012年，卢旺达与乌干达和刚果民主共和国的关系都已经得到改善<ref name="Heuler-2011" /><ref name="BBC News (VII)-2011">{{cite news | author = BBC News (VII) | date = 2011-11-03 | title = Rwanda gives DR Congo back tonnes of smuggled minerals | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-15570648 | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120425041024/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-15570648 | archivedate = 2012-04-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

