卢旺达自殖民时代以前就一直存在着严格的等级制度<ref name="OAU-2000">{{cite web |author=Organization of African Unity (OAU) |year=2000 |title=Rwanda – The preventable genocide |work=The Report of International Panel of Eminent Personalities to Investigate the 1994 Genocide in Rwanda and Surrounding Events |page=14 |url=http://www.aegistrust.org/images/stories/oaureport.pdf |accessdate=2014-04-16 |format=PDF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908042110/http://www.aegistrust.org/images/stories/oaureport.pdf |archivedate=2015-09-08 }}</ref>。殖民化前，卢旺达国王（当地人称“{{lang|rw|Mwami}}”）通过省、区、街区等体系来控制全国<ref name="Melvern-2004">{{cite book | last = Melvern | first = Linda | year = 2004 | title = Conspiracy to Murder: The Rwandan Genocide | edition = Revised | location = London; New York, N.Y. | publisher = Verso Books | isbn = 978-1-85984-588-2 | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=3NXIHf0t3aMC | page = 5 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201001103045/https://books.google.com/books?id=3NXIHf0t3aMC | archivedate = 2020-10-01 }}</ref>。现行宪法将卢旺达划分成[[卢旺达行政区划|省]]（{{lang|rw|intara}}）、[[市辖区|市辖区]]（{{lang|rw|uturere}}）、城市、[[基层政权|市]]、[[镇|镇]]、区（{{lang|rw|imirenge}}）、乡（{{lang|rw|utugari}}）和[[村_(行政区划)|村]]（{{lang|rw|imidugudu}}），较大的行政区划及其边界由议会设立<ref name="CJCR-2003" />{{rp|3}}。

整个国家共划分成五个省，相当于国家政策和组成各省的市辖区之间的中介，确保国家政策可以在地区层面上得到执行。根据地方政府部制定的“卢旺达分权战略框架”，各省有职责“协调省内治理工作并加以监督和评估”<ref name ="MINALOC-2007">{{cite web | author = Ministry of Local Government (MINALOC), Republic of Rwanda | date = 2007-08 | title = Rwanda Decentralization Strategic Framework | url = http://www.minecofin.gov.rw/webfm_send/2014 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130329024025/http://www.minecofin.gov.rw/webfm_send/2014 | archivedate = 2013-03-29 | accessdate = 2013-03-29 }}</ref>{{rp|8}}。每个省由[[省长|省长]]领导，省长由总统任命，但需经参议院确认<ref name="Southern Province">{{cite web | author = Southern Province | title = Governor | url = http://www.southernprovince.gov.rw/spip.php?article88 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130605143227/http://www.southernprovince.gov.rw/spip.php?article88 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-06-05 | accessdate = 2013-06-05 }}</ref>。市辖区负责协调公共服务和经济发展，其下又分成区，负责提供市辖区规定的公共服务<ref name ="MINALOC-2007" />{{rp|9}}。市辖区和区都拥有直接选举产生的议会，其行政部门就是议会选出的执行委员会<ref name="MINALOC-2004">{{cite web | author = Ministry of Local Government (MINALOC), Republic of Rwanda | year = 2004 | title = Administrative Units | archivedate = 2013-10-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131022061048/http://www.minaloc.gov.rw/index.php?id=450 | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | url = http://www.minaloc.gov.rw/index.php?id=450 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。乡和村是最小的政治单位，用来提供公民和区之间联系的桥梁<ref name ="MINALOC-2007" />{{rp|9}}。所有成年公民都是其所在乡村议会的成员，这个议会中将选出执行委员会成员<ref name="MINALOC-2004" />。国家[[首都|首都]][[基加利|基加利]]属省级行政区，负责协调全市范围内的城市规划<ref name ="MINALOC-2007" />{{rp|8}}。

卢旺达现行的行政区划分界于2006年划分，目标是下放权力并消除旧体制和种族灭绝的影响。之前全国划分为12个省，各省均以其最大的城市为核心，新的划分则主要依据地理方位为基准，全国只分成五个省，分别是[[北部省_(卢旺达)|北部省]]、[[南部省_(卢旺达)|南部省]]、[[东部省_(卢旺达)|东部省]]、[[西部省_(卢旺达)|西部省]]以及中部的基加利市。<ref name="BBC News (I)-2006">{{cite news | author = BBC News (I) | date = 2006-01-03 | title = Rwanda redrawn to reflect compass | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/4577790.stm | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140108171556/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/4577790.stm | archivedate = 2014-01-08 }}</ref>

