卢旺达的国土面积为26,338[[平方公里|平方公里]]，在世界各国中名列第149位<ref name="CIA (II)">{{cite web | author = Central Intelligence Agency (CIA) (II) | work = The World Factbook | title = Rank Order – Area | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140209041128/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2147rank.html | url = https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2147rank.html | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archivedate = 2014-02-09 }}</ref>，与布隆迪、[[马其顿|马其顿]]、[[海地|海地]]和[[阿尔巴尼亚|阿尔巴尼亚]]面积接近<ref name="CIA (II)" /><ref name="CIA (I)" /><ref name="Richards-1994">{{cite news | last = Richards | first = Charles | date = 1994-07-24 | title = Rwanda: Question Time: How could it happen?: Rebellion, slaughter, exodus, cholera: the catastrophe in Rwanda is beyond our worst imaginings. Who is to blame? Who are the Hutus and Tutsis? Can peace ever be restored? Some answers ... | work = The Independent | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | location = London | archivedate = 2014-02-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140226214246/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/rwanda-question-time-how-could-it-happen-rebellion-slaughter-exodus-cholera-the-catastrophe-in-rwanda-is-beyond-our-worst-imaginings-who-is-to-blame-who-are-the-hutus-and-tutsis-can-peace-ever-be-restored-some-answers-1415794.html | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/rwanda-question-time-how-could-it-happen-rebellion-slaughter-exodus-cholera-the-catastrophe-in-rwanda-is-beyond-our-worst-imaginings-who-is-to-blame-who-are-the-hutus-and-tutsis-can-peace-ever-be-restored-some-answers-1415794.html }}</ref>。整个国家都处在高海拔地区：最低点[[鲁济济河|鲁济济河]]也高于海平面950米<ref name="CIA (I)" />。卢旺达地处非洲中东部，西接刚果民主共和国，北邻乌干达，东面和[[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]]接壤，南部与布隆迪交界<ref name="CIA (I)" />，国家处在[[赤道|赤道]]以南几个纬度范围内，属[[内陆国家|内陆国家]]<ref name="Department of State (III)-2012" />。首都基加利位于该国中心附近<ref name="Encyclopædia Britannica-2010">{{cite web | author = Encyclopædia Britannica | year = 2010 | title = Rwanda | url = http://global.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/514402/Rwanda | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20131030165456/http://global.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/514402/Rwanda | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archivedate = 2013-10-30 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

[[刚果盆地|刚果盆地]]和[[尼罗河|尼罗河]][[流域|流域]]之间的[[刚果河和尼罗河分水岭|分水岭]]从北向南穿过卢旺达，国内约80%的区域从尼罗河引流，另外约20%则从[[鲁济济河|鲁济济河]]和[[坦干依喀湖|坦干依喀湖]]取水<ref name="Nile Basin Initiative-2010">{{cite web |author=Nile Basin Initiative |year=2010 |title=Nile Basin Countries |archivedate=2014-02-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228031357/http://nilebasin.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=48%3Anbi-country-profiles&catid=35%3Anbi-country-profiles&Itemid=67&lang=en |accessdate=2014-04-16 |url=http://nilebasin.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=48%253Anbi-country-profiles&catid=35%253Anbi-country-profiles&Itemid=67&lang=en }}</ref>。该国最长的河是源于西南部的[[尼亚巴隆哥河|尼亚巴隆哥河]]（{{lang|en|Nyabarongo River}}），分别朝北、东和东南方向转向后流入[[鲁武武河|鲁武武河]]并形成[[卡盖拉河|卡盖拉河]]，卡盖拉河将沿坦桑尼亚东部边境流向正北方。尼亚巴隆哥河与卡盖拉河最终都将流入[[维多利亚湖|维多利亚湖]]，有观点认为其位于纽格威森林的源头也是尚未完全确定的尼罗河的源头<ref name="BBC News (II)-2006">{{cite news | author = BBC News (II) | date = 2006-03-31 | title = Team reaches Nile's 'true source' | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/hampshire/4864782.stm | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131110122006/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/hampshire/4864782.stm | archivedate = 2013-11-10 }}</ref>。卢旺达湖泊众多，其中以[[基伏湖|基伏湖]]最大。该湖位于艾伯丁裂谷底部，沿卢旺达西部边境延伸，最深处有480米<ref name="Jørgensen-2005">{{cite book | last = Jørgensen | first = Sven Erik | year = 2005 | title = Lake and reservoir management | location = Amsterdam | publisher = Elsevier | isbn = 978-0-444-51678-7 | page = 93 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=pcJoaA85A48C | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200728133620/https://books.google.com/books?id=pcJoaA85A48C | archivedate = 2020-07-28 }}</ref>，是世界上最深的20个湖之一<ref name="Briggs-Booth-2006">{{cite book | last1 = Briggs | first1 = Philip | last2 = Booth | first2 = Janice | year = 2006 | title = Rwanda – The Bradt Travel Guide | edition = 3rd | location = London | publisher = Bradt Travel Guides | isbn = 978-1-84162-180-7 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=L2Sq4S3P5fQC | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200812193551/https://books.google.com/books?id=L2Sq4S3P5fQC | archivedate = 2020-08-12 }}</ref>{{rp|153}}。其它几个面积较大的湖泊包括布雷拉湖（{{lang|en|Lake Burera}}）、儒洪多湖（{{lang|en|Lake Ruhondo}}）、[[木哈子湖|木哈子湖]]（{{lang|en|Lake Muhazi}}）、鲁韦鲁湖（{{lang|en|Lake Rweru}}）和艾希玛湖（{{lang|en|Lake Ihema}}），其中艾希玛湖是[[阿卡盖拉国家公园|阿卡盖拉国家公园]]东部平原一系列湖泊中最大的一个<ref name="Global Nature Fund">{{cite web | author = Global Nature Fund | title = Lake Ihema | archivedate = 2014-01-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140107053244/http://www.globalnature.org/30036/LIVING-LAKES/National-Networks/Network-East-Africa/Ihema/02_vorlage.asp | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | url = http://www.globalnature.org/30036/LIVING-LAKES/National-Networks/Network-East-Africa/Ihema/02_vorlage.asp }}</ref>。

[[File:RwandaVolcanoAndLake_cropped2.jpg|thumb]]的湖泊和火山。]]
卢旺达的中西部以山区为主，这些山脉是艾伯丁裂谷山脉的一部分，而艾伯丁裂谷又是[[东非大裂谷|东非大裂谷]]的组成部分，沿卢旺达西部边境从北向南延伸<ref name="WWF-2001">{{cite web | author = World Wide Fund for Nature (WWF) | year = 2001 | title = Terrestrial Ecoregions: Albertine Rift montane forests (AT0101) | url = https://secure.worldwildlife.org/wildworld/profiles/terrestrial/at/at0101_full.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2004-12-22 | accessdate = 2012-02-16 | chapter = Location and General Description | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20041222014550/https://secure.worldwildlife.org/wildworld/profiles/terrestrial/at/at0101_full.html }}</ref>。境内最高的山位于西北部的[[维龙加山脉|维龙加山脉]]火山链，其中[[卡里辛比火山|卡里辛比火山]]高4507米，是卢旺达的地理最高点<ref name="Mehta-Katee-2005">{{cite web | last1 = Mehta | first1 = Hitesh | last2 = Katee | first2 = Christine | year = 2005 | title = Virunga Massif Sustainable Tourism Development Plan | publisher = International Gorilla Conservation Programme (IGCP) | deadurl = yes | page = 37 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140304055030/http://www.igcp.org/wp-content/themes/igcp/docs/pdf/VirungaTourismMasterPlan_%20Final%20Report.pdf | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | archivedate = 2014-03-04 | url = http://www.igcp.org/wp-content/themes/igcp/docs/pdf/VirungaTourismMasterPlan_%20Final%20Report.pdf }}</ref>。该国西部这段位于[[艾伯丁裂谷山地森林|艾伯丁裂谷山地森林]]生态区内的山区<ref name="WWF-2001" />海拔高度在1500至2500米之间<ref name="Munyakazi-Ntagaramba-2005">{{cite book | last1 = Munyakazi | first1 = Augustine | last2 = Ntagaramba | first2 = Johnson Funga | year = 2005 | title = Atlas of Rwanda | location = Oxford | publisher = Macmillan Education | isbn = 0-333-95451-3}}</ref>{{rp|7}}。卢旺达中部以连绵起伏的丘陵为主，东部边境地区则由[[热带草原|热带草原]]、平原和沼泽组成<ref name="Munyakazi-Ntagaramba-2005" />{{rp|18}}。

卢旺达属[[温带|温带]]和[[热带气候|热带高原]]气候，由于海拔较高，其气温比典型的赤道国家要低<ref name="Department of State (III)-2012" />。位于该国中部的基加利日常温度一般在12至27[[摄氏度|°C]]之间，全年波动幅度较小<ref name="BBC Weather">{{cite news | author = BBC Weather | title = Kigali | archivedate = 2011-10-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111011010121/http://news.bbc.co.uk/weather/forecast/782 | deadurl = yes | work = BBC News | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/weather/forecast/782 | accessdate = 2012-02-16 | chapter = Average Conditions }}</ref>。全国范围内也有一些地方温差较大，多山的西部和北部比东部低洼地区的气温要低<ref name="Best Country Reports-2007">{{cite web | author = Best Country Reports | year = 2007 | title = Temperature Map of Rwanda | publisher = World Trade Press | url = http://www.bestcountryreports.com/Temperature_Map_Rwanda.php | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121117203642/http://www.bestcountryreports.com/Temperature_Map_Rwanda.php | archivedate = 2012-11-17 }}</ref>。卢旺达每年有两个雨季，每一个从2月持续到6月，第二个从9月到10月；同时也有两个[[旱季|旱季]]，其中6到9月这个持续时间较长，经常完全没有降水，另一个则是从12月持续到次年2月，相对来说情况不及前一个那么严重<ref name="King 2007" />{{rp|10}}。降雨量因地域而不同，每年西部和西北部降水较东部和东南部为多<ref name="Adekunle-2007">{{cite book | last = Adekunle | first = Julius | year = 2007 | title = Culture and customs of Rwanda | location = Westport, Conn. | publisher = Greenwood Press | isbn = 978-0-313-33177-0 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=g0FC40EQujwC | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200812012619/https://books.google.com/books?id=g0FC40EQujwC | archivedate = 2020-08-12 }}</ref>{{rp|1}}。不过，雨季模式已因气候变化而出现变动。战略前瞻组织的一份报告中称，每年阴雨天数有时会变少，但短时间内的降雨量更大。还有些情况下单一天内就会频繁出现倾盆大雨，降雨量超过以往一个月的总和。此外还存在雨季姗姗来迟或是提早结束的情况<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.strategicforesight.com/publication_pdf/84153Blue%20Peace%20for%20the%20Nile.pdf | title = Blue Peace for the Nile, 2009 | author = Strategic Foresight Group | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140226155440/http://www.strategicforesight.com/publication_pdf/84153Blue%20Peace%20for%20the%20Nile.pdf | archivedate = 2014-02-26 }}</ref>。

