=== 生物多样性 ===
[[File:Akagera_1980_1_Topi.jpg|thumb]]生活的[[转角牛羚|转角牛羚]]。]]
如今的卢旺达境内在史前时期有三分之一属于[[山地生态|山地生态]]。目前天然存在的植物已基本局限在该国的三个[[国家公园|国家公园]]内，全国其它地区则以[[梯田|梯田农业]]占主导地位<ref name="Briggs-Booth-2006" />{{rp|3-4}}。[[纽格威国家公园|纽格威森林]]是现存最大的树林，内有200种树种，还拥有[[兰科|兰花]]和[[秋海棠属|海棠]]<ref name="King 2007" />{{rp|11}}。[[卢旺达火山国家公园|卢旺达火山国家公园]]的植物以[[竹|竹]]以主，剩下的大部分是高沼地，还有小面积的树木<ref name="Briggs-Booth-2006" />{{rp|3-4}}。阿卡盖拉国家公园则属热带草原生态系统，所有植物中以[[金合欢|金合欢]]最多，并且也有一些稀有或濒危的植物物种，如[[猫尾树|猫尾树]]和[[几内亚鸡冠兰|几内亚鸡冠兰]]等<ref name="REMA (Chapter 5)-2009">{{cite web |author=Rwanda Environment Management Authority (REMA) (Chapter 5) |year=2009 |title=Chap V. Biodiversity and Genetic Resources |work=Rwanda State of Environment and Outlook Report |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911104855/http://www.rema.gov.rw/soe/chap5.php |url=http://www.rema.gov.rw/soe/chap5.php |accessdate=2014-04-17 |archivedate=2013-09-11 }}</ref>。

三个国家公园中所发现的大型[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]种类也是最多的，公园也均属于指定保护区<ref name="IUCN-2011">{{cite web |author=International Union for Conservation of Nature (IUCN) |year=2011 |title=IUCN welcomes Rwanda as new State Member |archivedate=2012-03-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319150918/http://www.iucn.org/about/union/commissions/wcpa/?7308%2FIUCN-welcomes-Rwanda-as-new-State-Member |7= |accessdate=2012-02-16 |url=http://www.iucn.org/about/union/commissions/wcpa/?7308/IUCN-welcomes-Rwanda-as-new-State-Member }}</ref>。阿卡盖拉国家公园拥有包括[[长颈鹿|长颈鹿]]和[[大象|大象]]在内的典型稀树草原动物<ref name="Embassy of Rwanda in Japan">{{cite web | author = Embassy of Rwanda in Japan | title = Akagera National Park | url = http://japan.embassy.gov.rw/content/view/92/65/ | accessdate = 2012-02-29 | archivedate = 2013-06-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130603061218/http://japan.embassy.gov.rw/content/view/92/65 }}</ref>，而火山国家公园则是世界上约三分之一山地大猩猩的栖息地<ref name="RDB (II)-2010">{{cite web | author = Rwanda Development Board (RDB) (II) | date = 2010-05-07 | title = World Environment Day & Kwita Izina | archivedate = 2012-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120112140142/http://www.rwandatourism.com/test/contentdetail.php?tbl=press&serial=6&PHPSESSID=f991fb81d778f37460c75c17dcf18eb7 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2012-02-16 | url = http://www.rwandatourism.com/test/contentdetail.php?tbl=press&serial=6&PHPSESSID=f991fb81d778f37460c75c17dcf18eb7 }}</ref>。纽格威森林公园拥有包括[[黑猩猩属|黑猩猩]]和[[疣猴属|鲁文佐里树栖疣猴]]在内的13种[[灵长目|灵长类]]动物，其中鲁文佐里树栖疣猴会有多达400只进行群体活动，数量上超过非洲的其他任何灵长类动物<ref name="Briggs-Booth-2006" />{{rp|140}}。

卢旺达境内生活有670种鸟类，从东到西分布的种类有所不同<ref name="King 2007" />{{rp|15}}。西边的纽格威森林发现过280种，其中包括鲁文佐里蕉鹃和艳鹧鸪在内的26种为艾伯丁裂谷特有<ref name="WCS">{{cite web | author = Wildlife Conservation Society (WCS) | title = Birds endemic to the Albertine Rift | work = Albertine Rift Programme | url = http://www.albertinerift.org/portals/49/media/file/endemicbirds.PDF | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130624212609/http://www.albertinerift.org/portals/49/media/file/endemicbirds.PDF | archivedate = 2013-06-24 }}</ref><ref name="King 2007" />{{rp|15}}。卢旺达东部则拥有如乌头黑伯劳之类的稀树草原鸟类，以及习惯生活在沼泽和湖泊地区的物种，如[[鹳科|鹳]]和[[鹤科|鹤]]等<ref name="King 2007" />{{rp|15}}。

== 经济 ==
[[File:MarabaCoffeeDryingRacks.jpg|thumb]]是卢旺达的主要经济作物之一，图为正在烘干的[[马拉巴咖啡|马拉巴]]咖啡豆。]]
{{Main|盧旺達經濟}}
卢旺达的经济曾在1994年的种族灭绝期间遭受重创，大批平民遭到屠杀，基础设施严重受损，打家劫舍时有发生，重要的经济作物也被忽视。这些因素相结合，共同导致该国[[国内生产总值|国内生产总值]]大幅下跌，并且也无法吸收到私人和外来投资<ref name="CIA (I)" />。这以后卢旺达的经济逐渐复苏，根据[[国际货币基金组织|国际货币基金组织]]的统计数据，2015年估计该国的人均GDP（[[国际汇率|国际汇率]]）已经达到731[[美元|美元]]<ref name=imf2 />。主要的出口市场包括[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]、[[德国|德国]]和[[美国|美国]]<ref name="CIA (I)" />。国家的[[中央银行|中央银行]]是[[卢旺达国家银行|卢旺达国家银行]]，通行货币为[[卢旺达法郎|卢旺达法郎]]。截至2014年4月17日，卢旺达法郎对[[美元|美元]]的汇率为每680.48卢旺达法郎兑换1[[美元|美元]]<ref name="Exchange-RWF-USD">{{cite web | title = 换算USD(美元)到RWF(卢旺达法郎) | url = http://cn.exchange-rates.org/Rate/USD/RWF | publisher = MBH Media, Inc. | work = Exchange-Rates.org | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140419014825/http://cn.exchange-rates.org/Rate/USD/RWF | archivedate = 2014-04-19 }}</ref>。卢旺达于2007年加入东非共同体，并且有计划从2015年开始使用所有成员国通用的[[东非先令|东非先令]]<ref name="Lavelle-2008">{{cite news | last = Lavelle | first = John | date = 2008-07-05 | title = Resurrecting the East African Shilling | work = allAfrica.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121007163057/http://allafrica.com/stories/200807071183.html | archivedate = 2012-10-07 | url = http://allafrica.com/stories/200807071183.html | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

卢旺达自然资源匮乏<ref name="Department of State (III)-2012" />，经济主要依靠地方农民使用简单工具的[[自给农业|自给农业]]支撑<ref name="FAO / WFP-1997">{{cite web | author = Food and Agriculture Organization / World Food Programme (FAO / WFP) | date = 1997-07-01 | title = Special Report: FAO/WFP Crop and Food Supply Assessment Mission to Rwanda | url = http://www.fao.org/docrep/004/w5836e/w5836e00.htm | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archivedate = 2013-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002010045/http://www.fao.org/docrep/004/w5836e/w5836e00.htm | deadurl = no }}</ref>。根据估算，2010年国内生产总值的42.1%是由90%的工作人口通过务农创造的<ref name="CIA (I)" />。自20世纪80年代中期开始，农场规模和粮食产量都有所下降，这部分是因为需要占用土地安置失去家园的人们<ref name=WRI-2006>{{cite web | author = World Resources Institute (WRI) | year = 2006 | title = Agriculture and Food: Country profile – Rwanda | work = EarthTrends: The Environmental Information Portal | archivedate = 2012-04-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120402134313/http://earthtrends.wri.org/text/agriculture-food/country-profile-153.html | url = http://earthtrends.wri.org/text/agriculture-food/country-profile-153.html | accessdate = 2012-04-02 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref name="Department of State (I)-2004">{{cite web | author = Department of State (I) | year = 2004 | title = Background Note: Rwanda | work = Background Notes | url = http://www.state.gov/outofdate/bgn/rwanda/40249.htm | accessdate = 2012-02-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140114124207/http://www.state.gov/outofdate/bgn/rwanda/40249.htm | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-01-14 }}</ref>。虽然卢旺达土地肥沃，但粮食产量往往跟不上人口增速，因此必须进口粮食<ref name="CIA (I)" />。

卢旺达种植的作物包括咖啡、茶叶、[[除虫菊|除虫菊]]、[[香蕉|香蕉]]、[[豆类|豆类]]、[[高粱属|高粱]]和[[马铃薯|土豆]]。咖啡和茶叶是主要的出口经济作物，较高的地势、陡峭的山坡和肥沃的火山土壤为其生长提供了有利条件。过于依赖农产品出口使得卢旺达的经济对价格变化非常敏感<ref name="WTO-2004">{{cite web | author = World Trade Organization (WTO) | date = 2004-09-30 | title = Continued reforms and technical assistance should help Rwanda in its efforts to achieve a dynamic economy | work = Trade policy review: Rwanda | url = http://www.wto.org/english/tratop_e/tpr_e/tp236_e.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002011128/http://www.wto.org/english/tratop_e/tpr_e/tp236_e.htm | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2012-02-16 | archivedate = 2013-10-02 }}</ref>。卢旺达饲养的动物包括[[牛|牛]]、[[山羊|山羊]]、[[绵羊|绵羊]]、[[家猪|猪]]、[[鸡|鸡]]和[[兔|兔]]，数量因地而异<ref name="MINAGRI-2006">{{cite web | author = Ministry of Agriculture (MINAGRI), Republic of Rwanda | date = 2006-06-10 | title = Livestock production | archivedate = 2012-05-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120513150307/http://www.minagri.gov.rw/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=156%3Alivestock&Itemid=48&lang=en | url = http://www.minagri.gov.rw/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=156%3Alivestock&Itemid=48&lang=en | accessdate = 2012-05-13 }}</ref>。除了基加利周边有几家密集型奶牛养殖场外，其他地区基本沿用传统的养殖手段<ref name="MINAGRI-2006" />。土地和水资源不足、饲料质量差、定期出现的疫情以及[[兽医|兽医]]数量不足都是限制动物产量提高的主要因素。国内多个湖泊存在渔业，但鱼量已所剩无几，为此该国正从国外进口活鱼，希望能重振产业<ref name="Namata-2008">{{cite news | last = Namata | first = Berna | date = 2008-12-28 | title = Rwanda to restock water bodies with fisheries | publisher = The New Times | url = http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/views/article_print.php?13758&a=1108&week=45 | accessdate = 2013-11-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131107061636/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/views/article_print.php?13758&a=1108&week=45 | archivedate = 2013-11-07 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

卢旺达的工业规模较小，只占2010年{{lang|en|GDP}}的14.3%<ref name="CIA (I)" />。生产的产品包括[[水泥|水泥]]、农产品、小瓶饮料、[[肥皂|肥皂]]、[[家具|家具]]、鞋类、塑料制品、[[纺织品|纺织品]]和[[香烟|香烟]]<ref name="CIA (I)" />。采矿业是重要的出口产业，根据2008年的统计数据，全国通过矿产出口获得了9300万美元的收入<ref name="Mukaaya-2009">{{cite news | last = Mukaaya | first = Eddie | date = 2009-01-15 | title = Mining industry generated $93 million in 2008 | work = The New Times | location = Kigali | url = http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=13776&a=12470 | accessdate = 2013-11-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131107064530/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=13776&a=12470 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-11-07 }}</ref>。国内主要开采的矿产包括[[锡石|锡石]]、[[黑钨|黑钨]]、[[金|金]]和[[钶钽铁矿|钶钽铁矿]]，其中最后一种主要用于制造包括[[移动电话|移动电话]]在内的多种电子和通讯设备<ref name="Mukaaya-2009" /><ref name="Delawala-2001">{{cite news | last = Delawala | first = Imtiyaz | date = 2001-09-07 | title = What Is Coltan? | work = ABC News: Nightline | url = http://abcnews.go.com/Nightline/story?id=128631&page=1 | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131008174825/http://abcnews.go.com/Nightline/story?id=128631&page=1 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-10-08 }}</ref>。位在[[基加利|基加利]]的[[卡路魯馬冶煉廠|卡路魯馬冶煉廠]]以往曾有錫礦的冶煉，目前由魯納冶煉有限公司營運，以礦石交易為主<ref>{{cite news | last = Iliza | first = Ange | date = 2020-09-08 | title = How mining sector could drive up revenue | work = ABC News: Nightline | url = https://www.newtimes.co.rw/business/how-mining-sector-could-drive-revenue | accessdate = 2020-10-23 | archive-date = 2021-02-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210208170710/https://www.newtimes.co.rw/business/how-mining-sector-could-drive-revenue | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[File:Gorilla_mother_and_baby_at_Volcans_National_Park.jpg|thumb]]的[[山地大猩猩|山地大猩猩]]。]]
卢旺达的[[第三产业|第三产业]]在[[经济大衰退|经济大衰退]]期间受到打击，银行贷款和外援项目及资金都有所减少<ref name="Nantaba-2010">{{cite news | last = Nantaba | first = Eriosi | date = 2010-10-18 | title = Rwanda services sector boosts GDP | work = allAfrica.com | url = http://allafrica.com/stories/201010181360.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019130336/http://allafrica.com/stories/201010181360.html | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。不过到了2010年时，其所占经济比重已居全国首位，贡献了43.6%的{{lang|en|GDP}}<ref name="CIA (I)" />。其中表现较为突出的行业包括银行和金融业、批发和零售业、住宿和餐饮业、交通运输、仓储、通讯、保险、房地产、商务服务和包括教育与卫生在内的公共管理业<ref name="Nantaba-2010" />。卢旺达的[[旅游业|旅游业]]增长迅猛，2011年时已成为该国最重要的外汇收入来源<ref name="Birakwate-2012">{{cite news | last = Birakwate | first = Bruno | date = 2012-03-26 | title = Google Maps to promote Rwanda's tourism | work = Rwanda Focus | url = http://focus.rw/wp/2012/03/google-maps-to-promote-rwandas-tourism/ | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130418052607/http://focus.rw/wp/2012/03/google-maps-to-promote-rwandas-tourism/ | archivedate = 2013-04-18 }}</ref>。尽管有过种族灭绝这样不光彩的过去，但国际上却越来越倾向于认为卢旺达是一个安全的好去处<ref name="Nielsen-Spenceley-2010">{{cite web | last1 = Nielsen | first1 = Hannah | last2 = Spenceley | first2 = Anna | date = 2010-04 | title = The success of tourism in Rwanda – Gorillas and more | work = African Success Stories Study | publisher = World Bank & SNV Netherlands Development Organisation | archivedate = 2014-03-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320185656/http://siteresources.worldbank.org/AFRICAEXT/Resources/258643-1271798012256/Tourism_Rwanda.pdf | accessdate = 2014-04-16 | url = http://siteresources.worldbank.org/AFRICAEXT/Resources/258643-1271798012256/Tourism_Rwanda.pdf }}</ref>{{rp|6}}。根据入境和移民署的统计，2011年1至6月共有40万5801人到访卢旺达，其中16%来自非洲以外的国家和地区<ref name="RDB (III)-2011">{{cite web | author = Rwanda Development Board (RDB) (III) | year = 2011 | title = Highlights of Tourist Arrivals in Rwanda January–June 2011 | archivedate = 2014-03-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320185756/http://www.rdb.rw/fileadmin/user_upload/Documents/tourism%20conservation/Arrival_Statistics_2011_1st_semester__version_2_.pdf | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | url = http://www.rdb.rw/fileadmin/user_upload/Documents/tourism%20conservation/Arrival_Statistics_2011_1st_semester__version_2_.pdf }}</ref>，这半年内的旅游业收入则达到1亿1560万美元，其中假日游客虽然人数只占9%，但却贡献了43%的消费<ref name="RDB (III)-2011" />。卢旺达是世界上仅有的两个可以安全看到山地大猩猩的国家之一，卢旺达火山国家公园提供的大猩猩追踪服务每年都吸引了成千上万甘愿支付高价获取许可证的游客<ref name="Nielsen-Spenceley-2010" />{{rp|2}}。该国的其他景点还包括纽格威森林，这里是黑猩猩、鲁文佐里树栖疣猴和其它灵长类动物的栖息地；基伍湖度假胜地，以及位于卢旺达东部的阿卡盖拉国家公园，这里是一片小规模的热带草原保护区<ref name="RDB (IV)">{{cite web |author=Rwanda Development Board (RDB) (IV) |title=National Parks |url=http://www.rwandatourism.com/parks.htm |accessdate=2012-03-01 |archivedate=2012-05-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120511234019/http://www.rwandatourism.com/parks.htm }}</ref>。

=== 媒体和通信 ===
卢旺达最大的广播电台和电视台都是国营的。大部分卢旺达人都能够收听电台广播，卢旺达广播电台则是整个国家主要的新闻来源，而电视则基本局限在城市地区<ref name="BBC News (V)-2011">{{cite news | author = BBC News (V) | date = 2011-11-25 | title = Rwanda country profile: Media | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-14093244 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140311051156/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-14093244 | archivedate = 2014-03-11 | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。新闻界受到严格的限制，报纸经常进行自我审查以免受到政府的报复<ref name="BBC News (V)-2011" />。不过，批评政府的卢旺达语、英语和法语出版物在基加利还是随处可见。2010年卢旺达总统选举期间，媒体受到的限制有所加强，当地名为“{{lang|en|Umuseso}}”和“{{lang|en|Umuvugizi}}”的两家主要独立报纸受到了高级媒体理事会停办六个月的惩罚<ref name="Reporters Without Borders-2010">{{cite web |author=Reporters Without Borders |date=2010-04-14 |title=Two leading independent weeklies suspended for six months |url=http://en.rsf.org/rwanda-two-leading-independent-weeklies-14-04-2010,37015.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624234654/http://en.rsf.org/rwanda-two-leading-independent-weeklies-14-04-2010%2C37015.html |accessdate=2014-04-17 |archivedate=2013-06-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

卢旺达电信（{{lang|en|Rwandatel}}）是成立最早的电信集团，向约2.3万用户提供[[固网电信|固网电信]]服务，其中大部分是政府机构、银行、[[非政府组织|非政府组织]]和大使馆<ref name="Majyambere-2010">{{cite news | last = Majyambere | first = Gertrude | date = 2010-05-14 | title = Rwandatel's Landline Telephony Increases By 7 Percent | work = The New Times | location = Kigali | url = http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14260&a=29114 | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archivedate = 2013-11-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131107055916/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14260&a=29114 }}</ref>。全国的私人座机订购率很低，移动电话普及率相对较高，已从2011年的35%<ref name="Butera-2011-03">{{cite news | last = Butera | first = Saul | date = 2011-03-17 | title = Mobile subscribers rise 51% | work = The New Times | location = Kigali | url = http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14567&a=39259 | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131107071623/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14567&a=39259 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-11-07 }}</ref>提高到2013年的57%<ref name="BiztechAfrica-2013">{{cite news | author = BiztechAfrica | date = 2013-05-01 | title = Rwanda mobile penetration tops 57% | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130607120253/http://www.biztechafrica.com/article/rwanda-mobile-penetration-tops-57/5909/ | url = http://www.biztechafrica.com/article/rwanda-mobile-penetration-tops-57/5909/ | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archivedate = 2013-06-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[MTN集团|MTN]]}}拥有约250万用户，是该国最大的移动电话服务提供商，其次是拥有70万用户的{{lang|en|[[米雷康姆|Tigo]]}}<ref name="Butera-2011-03" />。2012年3月，[[巴帝电信|巴帝电信]]成为卢旺达的第三家移动电话服务提供商<ref name="India Tech Online-2012">{{cite news | author = India Tech Online | date = 2012-03-31 | title = Airtel launches operations in Rwanda, in 83 days: fastest Greenfield launch in history of Sub-Saharan Africa | url = http://www.indiatechonline.com/it-happened-in-india.php?id=725 | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archivedate = 2013-04-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130426033432/http://indiatechonline.com/it-happened-in-india.php?id=725 }}</ref>。卢旺达电信也曾也经营移动电话网络，但由于该公司没有做到之前许下的投资承诺，行业监管机构于2011年4月吊销了其执照<ref name="Butera-2011-04">{{cite news | last = Butera | first = Saul | date = 2011-04-06 | title = MTN, Tigo Reaping From Rwandatel Misery | work = The New Times | location = Kigali | archivedate = 2014-04-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140417152143/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14590&a=39889 | url = http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14590&a=39889 | accessdate = 2014-04-17 }}</ref>。卢旺达的互联网普及率很低，但增长迅速。2007年该国平均每100人中只有2.1位互联网用户，到2012年时已增长到8人<ref name="World Bank (II)">{{cite web | author = World Bank (II) | title = Internet users (per 100 people) | work = Data | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131120061540/http://data.worldbank.org/indicator/IT.NET.USER.P2?cid=GPD_44 | url = http://data.worldbank.org/indicator/IT.NET.USER.P2?cid=GPD_44 | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archivedate = 2013-11-20 }}</ref>。2011年，该国已架设了2300公里长的[[光导纤维|光纤]]电信网络，用来提供宽带服务并促进电子商务<ref name="Reuters-2011">{{cite news | author = Reuters | date = 2011-03-16 | title = Rwanda completes $95 mln fibre optic network | url = http://af.reuters.com/article/investingNews/idAFJOE72F07D20110316 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120918134732/http://af.reuters.com/article/investingNews/idAFJOE72F07D20110316 | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archivedate = 2012-09-18 }}</ref>。该网络连接到了{{lang|en|[[SEACOM_(电缆系统)|SEACOM]]}}，这是一家南部和东部非洲的[[海底电缆|海底光纤电缆]]通信运营商，其位于卢旺达境内的光缆则沿主要道路连接到全国各地的城镇<ref name="Reuters-2011" />。移动电话服务提供商{{lang|en|MTN}}还在基加利大部分地区提供预付费的{{lang|en|[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]}}服务<ref name="Butera-2010">{{cite news | last = Butera | first = Saul | date = 2010-01-09 | title = MTN Rwanda deploys new Internet technology | work = The New Times | location = Kigali | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131107065826/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14135&a=24621 | archivedate = 2013-11-07 | url = http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14135&a=24621 | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

=== 基础设施 ===
[[File:WaterPumpRwanda.jpg|thumb]]
进入21世纪后，卢旺达政府开始优先为供水需要提供资金，大幅增加了其在国家预算中所占比重<ref name="IDA-2009">{{cite web |author=International Development Association (IDA) |title=Rwanda: Bringing Clean Water to Rural Communities |archivedate=2012-11-01 |accessdate=2014-04-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121101145742/http://web.worldbank.org/WBSITE/EXTERNAL/EXTABOUTUS/IDA/0%2C%2CcontentMDK%3A21256336~menuPK%3A3266877~pagePK%3A51236175~piPK%3A437394~theSitePK%3A73154%2C00.html |url=http://web.worldbank.org/WBSITE/EXTERNAL/EXTABOUTUS/IDA/0,,contentMDK:21256336~menuPK:3266877~pagePK:51236175~piPK:437394~theSitePK:73154,00.html }}</ref>。这些拨款加上一些捐款，令该国的饮用水品质得到大幅改善。2005年时，全国55%的人口可以获得清洁的水源，到了2008年则已提高到73%<ref name="IDA-2009" />。该国的供水基础设施分城市和农村两种类别，其中城市大多采用私人连接，农村则以竖管为主。没有这些设施的地区则会使用手动水泵和有人管理的泉水<ref name="MINECOFIN-2002">{{cite web | author = Ministry of Finance and Economic Planning (MINECOFIN), Republic of Rwanda | date = 2002-06 | title = Poverty Reduction Strategy Paper | url = http://www.imf.org/external/np/prsp/2002/rwa/01/063102.pdf | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023191649/http://www.imf.org/external/np/prsp/2002/rwa/01/063102.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | pages = 25-26 | format = PDF }}</ref>。虽然有许多地区的年降雨量在1000毫米以上<ref name="BBC Weather" />，但可用于收集雨水的设施很少<ref name="MINECOFIN-2002" />。[[卢旺达供水和卫生设施|卫生设施]]仍旧匮乏，联合国估计截至2006年时，仍然只有34%的城市居民和20%的农村居民能够使用得到改善的卫生设施<ref name="USAID-2008">{{cite web | author = United States Agency for International Development (USAID) | year = 2008 | title = Rwanda: Water and Sanitation Profile | page = 3 | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029123859/http://pdf.usaid.gov/pdf_docs/PNADO938.pdf | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | url = http://pdf.usaid.gov/pdf_docs/PNADO938.pdf | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。政府政策中用于改善卫生设施的也相当有限，只能关注城市地区<ref name="USAID-2008" />。无论是生活在城市还是农村的大部分人口使用的都是卫生条件很差的公共[[旱厕|旱厕]]<ref name="USAID-2008" />。

21世纪前，卢旺达的电力供应几乎完全来自[[水力发电|水力发电]]，建在布雷拉湖和儒洪多湖上的水电站提供全国90%的电力<ref name="World Resources Report-2011">{{cite web | author = World Resources Report | year = 2011 | title = Maintenance of Hydropower Potential in Rwanda Through Ecosystem Restoration | archivedate = 2013-06-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130605224537/http://www.worldresourcesreport.org/files/wrr/WRR%20Case%20Study_Ecosystem%20Restoration%20and%20Hydropower%20in%20Rwanda_0.pdf | format = PDF | accessdate = 2013-06-05 | url = http://www.worldresourcesreport.org/files/wrr/WRR%20Case%20Study_Ecosystem%20Restoration%20and%20Hydropower%20in%20Rwanda_0.pdf }}</ref>{{rp|3}}。1990年起，由于降雨量低于平均水平，并且还存在居民引水灌溉等人类活动因素的影响，两湖水位开始下降，到2004年时，水位已降低了50%，导致发电站产能大幅下跌<ref name="World Resources Report-2011" />{{rp|5}}，再加上经济增长带来的需求增长，全国出现了严重的电力短缺，不得不进行大范围的[[轮流停电|轮流停电]]<ref name="World Resources Report-2011" />{{rp|5}}。政府在基加利以北安装了[[柴油发电机|柴油发电机]]来作为紧急措施，到2006年时已经用于提供全国56%的电力，但这样的发电方式成本太高<ref name="World Resources Report-2011" />{{rp|5}}。政府还制定了多项措施来缓解这个问题，例如重新安置居民，向布雷拉湖和儒洪多湖供水，以及为从基伍湖中提取甲烷气体的项目进行投资等，其中最后一个项目的第一阶段预期将把全国发电量提升40%<ref name="AfDB-2011">{{cite web | author = African Development Bank (AfDB) | date = 2011-08-26 | title = Boosting Rwanda's Energy Sector: AfDB, other Lenders Commit USD 91.25 million to Kivuwatt Project | archivedate = 2013-01-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130105120930/http://www.afdb.org/en/news-and-events/article/boosting-rwandas-energy-sector-afdb-other-lenders-commit-usd-91-25-million-to-kivuwatt-project-8338/ | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | url = http://www.afdb.org/en/news-and-events/article/boosting-rwandas-energy-sector-afdb-other-lenders-commit-usd-91-25-million-to-kivuwatt-project-8338/ }}</ref>。截至2013年，全国能够用上电的人口仍然只有6%<ref name="MININFRA-2009">{{cite web | author = Ministry of Infrastructure (MININFRA), Republic of Rwanda | date = 2009-07 | title = Introduction to Energy sub sector | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140227092538/http://www.mininfra.gov.rw/25/ | quote = Increase connectivity from the current 6% to at least 16% of the population | url = http://www.mininfra.gov.rw/25/ | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | archivedate = 2014-02-27 }}</ref>。

1994年的种族灭绝后，卢旺达政府在中国、美国、[[欧洲联盟|欧盟]]及[[日本|日本]]等国家和组织的帮助下加大了对[[卢旺达交通|国内交通基础设施]]的投资力度,現今盧旺達大眾交通基礎設施多為中國企業承攬。交通系统以公路网络为主，通过铺面道路把基加利和全国其他大部分主要城市及城镇连接起来<ref name="AfDB-OECD Development Centre-2006">{{cite book | author1 = African Development Bank (AfDB) | author2 = Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development (OECD) Development Centre | year = 2006 | title = African Economic Outlook | edition = 5 | location = Paris | publisher = OECD Publishing | isbn = 978-92-64-02243-0 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=fpEFOR6WmfYC | page = 439 | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200728203640/https://books.google.com/books?id=fpEFOR6WmfYC | archivedate = 2020-07-28 }}</ref>。卢旺达通过公路连通了包括乌干达、坦桑尼亚、布隆迪和[[肯尼亚|肯尼亚]]在内的多个东非国家，还连接到了刚果东部城市[[戈马|戈马]]和[[布卡武|布卡武]]，该国最重要的贸易路线就是途经[[坎帕拉|坎帕拉]]和[[奈洛比|奈洛比]]到达[[蒙巴萨|蒙巴萨]]的道路<ref name="TTCA-2004">{{cite web | author = Transit Transport Coordination Authority of the Northern Corridor (TTCA) | date = 2004-06 | title = Investment Opportunities in the Northern Corridor with emphasis in Transport Infrastructure | publisher = OECD | archivedate = 2012-07-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120728094558/http://www.oecd.org/dataoecd/22/36/34879173.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.oecd.org/dataoecd/22/36/34879173.pdf | accessdate = 2014-04-17 }}</ref>。卢旺达的公共交通以[[合乘出租车|合乘出租车]]为主。主要城市间有快速公路连接，还会向主要道路的沿途大多数村庄提供地方服务。旅客可乘[[客车|长途汽车]]前往多个邻近国家的目的地。[[基加利国际机场|基加利国际机场]]是全国唯一的[[国际机场|国际机场]]，提供一条国内航线和多条国际航线服务<ref name="RwandAir">{{cite web | author = RwandAir | title = Flights Schedule | url = http://www.rwandair.com/plan-your-flight/schedule-map.html | accessdate = 2013-10-08 | archivedate = 2013-10-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131008103542/http://www.rwandair.com/plan-your-flight/schedule-map.html | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。截至2011年时，该国还没有[[铁路|铁路]]，但已进行拨款研究将坦桑尼亚的[[中央铁路_(坦桑尼亚)|中央线]]延长到本国境内的可行性<ref name="AfDB-2009">{{cite web | author = African Development Bank (AfDB) | date = 2009-11-19 | title = AfDB Approves Funding for Burundi-Rwanda-Tanzania Railway Project Study | archivedate = 2012-07-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120728201426/http://www.afdb.org/en/news-and-events/article/afdb-approves-funding-for-burundi-rwanda-tanzania-railway-project-study-5399/ | accessdate = 2014-02-16 | url = http://www.afdb.org/en/news-and-events/article/afdb-approves-funding-for-burundi-rwanda-tanzania-railway-project-study-5399/ }}</ref>，另外，该国也正在规划建设[[盧旺達標準軌鐵路|标准轨铁路]]<ref name="1R">{{cite web |url=http://www.newsofrwanda.com/featured2/32688/rwanda-bypasses-uganda-for-its-own-standard-gauge-railway-line/ |title=Rwanda Bypasses Uganda For Its Own Standard Gauge Railway Line |date=2018-01-15 |access-date=2018-09-19 |last=Mugabo |first=Peter |publisher=NewsofRwanda.com |location=Kigali |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207163237/http://www.newsofrwanda.com/featured2/32688/rwanda-bypasses-uganda-for-its-own-standard-gauge-railway-line/ |archivedate=2020-02-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。基伍湖和港口城市之间没有公共用水输送系统，不过有一些私营机构提供有限的相应服务，政府也已发起鼓励提供全方位服务的计划<ref name="AfDB-OECD Development Centre-2006" />。

== 人口 ==
[[File:Rwandan_children_at_Volcans_National_Park.jpg|thumb]]
截至2012年，卢旺达人口估计达到11,689,696人<ref name="CIA (I)" />，其结构以青年为主，估计15岁以下人数占到42.7%，65岁以下则有97.5%。全年人口出生率为每1,000人有40.2人，死亡率则是14.9<ref name="CIA (I)" />。预期寿命58.02年（女性59.52年、男性56.57年），在全世界223个国家和地区中名列第197位<ref name="CIA (I)" /><ref name="CIA (III)-2011">{{cite web | author = Central Intelligence Agency (CIA) (III) | year = 2011 | work = The World Factbook | title = Rank Order – Life expectancy at birth | url = https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2102rank.html | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120024054/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2102rank.html | archivedate = 2016-01-20 }}</ref>。全国的性别比则相对均衡<ref name="CIA (I)" />。

卢旺达是非洲人口密度最高的国家之一，平均每平方公里土地上生活了408位居民。历史学家热拉尔·普鲁尼尔（{{lang|fr|Gérard Prunier}}）认为，这样高的人口密度也是1994年种族灭绝的原因之一<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|4}}。全国人口大部分生活在农村，还有为数不多的一些城镇，人口分布相对均匀<ref name="Department of State (III)-2012" />，只有乌姆塔拉省（{{lang|en|Umutara}}，省份已不存在）的热带稀树草原和东部的阿卡盖拉国家公园人口稀少<ref name=Streissguth-2007>{{cite book | last = Streissguth | first = Thomas | year = 2007 | title = Rwanda in Pictures | location = Minneapolis, Minn. | publisher = Twenty-First Century Books | isbn = 978-0-8225-8570-1 | page = 11 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=Rfjw_5JL0DsC | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200812193550/https://books.google.com/books?id=Rfjw_5JL0DsC | archivedate = 2020-08-12 }}</ref>。基加利拥有约100万人口，是全国人口最多的城市<ref name="Kigali City">{{cite web |author=Kigali City |title=Kigali at a glance |archivedate=2014-02-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228100441/http://www.kigalicity.gov.rw/spip.php?article2 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.kigalicity.gov.rw/spip.php?article2 |accessdate=2014-04-18 }}</ref>。人口的快速增长使卢旺达的基礎建設不勝負荷<ref name="CIA (I)" /><ref name="Percival-Homer-Dixon-1995">{{cite journal | last1 = Percival | first1 = Valerie | last2 = Homer-Dixon | first2 = Thomas | year = 1995 | title = Environmental Scarcity and Violent Conflict, The Case of Rwanda | journal = Occasional Paper: Project on Environment, Population and Security | publisher = University of Toronto | url = http://www.library.utoronto.ca/pcs/eps/rwanda/rwanda1.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120916092722/http://www.library.utoronto.ca/pcs/eps/rwanda/rwanda1.htm | accessdate = 2012-09-16 | archivedate = 2012-09-16 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref name="REMA (Chapter 2)-2009">{{cite web | author = Rwanda Environment Management Authority (REMA) (Chapter 2) | year = 2009 | title = Chap II. Population, Health and human settlements | work = Rwanda State of Environment and Outlook Report | url = http://www.rema.gov.rw/soe/chap2.php | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130911104316/http://www.rema.gov.rw/soe/chap2.php | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-09-11 }}</ref>。其它几个较著名的城市有[[吉塔拉马|吉塔拉马]]、[[布塔雷市|布塔雷市]]和[[吉塞尼|吉塞尼]]，人口均少于10万<ref name="National Census Service 2003">{{cite web | author = National Census Service | date = 2003-02 | title = The General Census of Population and Housing, Rwanda | format = PDF | url = http://www.grandslacs.net/doc/2816.pdf | accessdate = 2012-02-16 | archivedate = 2012-12-23 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121223141314/http://www.grandslacs.net/doc/2816.pdf }}</ref>{{rp|26}}。1990年时，卢旺达的城市人口占比为6%<ref name="Percival-Homer-Dixon-1995" />，到2006年则提高到了16.6%<ref name="National Institute of Statistics of Rwanda-2012" />{{rp|29}}，不过，这个比例到2011年时又下跌到了14.8%<ref name="National Institute of Statistics of Rwanda-2012" />{{rp|29}}。

卢旺达从殖民时代前就一直是一个统一的国家<ref name="Appiah-Gates-2010" />，其人口均属[[巴尼亚卢旺达人|巴尼亚卢旺达人]]这一个民族和语言团体<ref name="Mamdani 2002" />{{rp|52}}；而现今大部分非洲国家的边界都是由[[非洲殖民地|殖民国家]]划分，并且没有对应的种族界限或前殖民时代王国<ref name="Boyd-1979">{{cite journal | last = Boyd | first = J. Barron | date = 1979-12 | title = African Boundary Conflict: An Empirical Study | journal = African Studies Review | issn = 0002-0206 | volume = 22 | issue = 3 | jstor = 523892 | page = 1}}</ref>。巴尼亚卢旺达人之中又主要分为三大族群，分别是胡图族（2009年时占总人口比例的84%）、图西族（占15%）和特瓦族（占1%）<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|5}}<ref name="CIA (I)" />。特瓦族是卢旺达最早居民俾格米人的后代，而学术界对胡图族和图西族的差异和起源尚未达成共識<ref name="Mamdani 2002" />{{rp|46-47}}。[[人类学|人类学家]]让·海恩纳克斯（{{lang|en|Jean Hiernaux}}）认为图西族属独立种族，其头、脸和鼻都较为狭长<ref name="Mamdani 2002" />{{rp|47}}，维里亚·杰弗里慕瓦斯（{{lang|en|Villia Jefremovas}}）则认为两个民族没有明显的生理差异，并且其分类也不是历史上所固有的<ref name="Jefremovas-1995">{{cite journal | last = Jefremovas | first = Villia | year = 1995 | title = Acts of Human Kindness: Tutsi, Hutu and the Genocide | journal = Issue: A Journal of Opinion | issn = 0047-1607 | volume = 23 | issue = 2 | pages = 28-31 | jstor = 1166503 | doi = 10.2307/1166503}}</ref>。殖民时代前，图西族是卢旺达地区的统治阶级，国王和大部分酋长都属该族，而胡图族人则以农耕为主<ref name="Prunier 1995" />{{rp|11-12}}。当今的卢旺达政府将身份证件上不同种族的分类去除，希望能够逐渐消除胡图族、图西族和特瓦族之间的差异<ref name="Coleman-2010">{{cite news | last = Coleman | first = Isobel | date = 2010-04-07 | title = Rwanda: Road to Recovery | work = The Huffington Post | url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/isobel-coleman/rwanda-road-to-recovery_b_529366.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131102190846/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/isobel-coleman/rwanda-road-to-recovery_b_529366.html | archivedate = 2013-11-02 | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

[[File:RwamaganaChurch.jpg|thumb]]的罗马天主教堂。]]
大多数卢旺达人都是天主教徒，但在种族灭绝后，全国的宗教人口分布已经有了显著变化，许多人皈依[[福音神学|福音]]基督教派或是[[伊斯兰教|伊斯兰教]]<ref name="Walker-2004-04">{{cite news | last = Walker | first = Robert | date = 2004-04-01 | title = Rwanda's religious reflections | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222133036/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/3561365.stm | deadurl = no | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/3561365.stm | work = BBC News | accessdate = 2014-04-16 }}</ref>。根据2006年的统计数据，全国56.5%的人口信奉[[天主教|天主教]]，37.1%是[[新教徒|新教徒]]（其中11.1%属[[基督复临安息日会|基督复临安息日会]]），还有4.6%的人口是[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]<ref name="Department of State (II)-2007">{{cite web | author = Department of State (II) | year = 2007 | title = Rwanda | work = International Religious Freedom Report 2007 | url = http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/irf/2007/90115.htm | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | archivedate = 2014-04-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140414101646/http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/irf/2007/90115.htm | deadurl = no }}</ref>，另外还有1.7%的人口声称自己没有宗教信仰<ref name="Department of State (II)-2007" />。传统宗教的正式信众仅占人口的千分之一，但仍有一定影响力。许多卢旺达人认为[[基督教中的神|基督教中的神]]与传统的卢旺达神明“伊玛纳”（{{lang|rw|Imana}}）实际上是相同的<ref name="Wiredu-Abraham-Irele-Menkiti-2006">{{cite book | last1 = Wiredu | first1 = Kwasi | last2 = Abraham | first2 = William E. | last3 = Irele | first3 = Abiola | last4 = Menkiti | first4 = Ifeanyi | year = 2006 | title = A companion to African philosophy | location = Malden, Mass. | pages = 236-237 | publisher = Wiley-Blackwell | isbn = 978-1-4051-4567-1 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=0HIbKtzjcQYC | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200812012621/https://books.google.com/books?id=0HIbKtzjcQYC | archivedate = 2020-08-12 }}</ref>。

卢旺达的主要语言是大部分卢旺达人都会说的[[卢旺达语|卢旺达语]]，殖民时代的主要欧洲语言先是[[德语|德语]]，然后是[[法语|法语]]，其中后者是由比利时人传入，并且直到卢旺达独立后仍然是广泛使用的官方语种<ref name="Université Laval-2010">{{cite web | author = Université Laval | year = 2010 | title = Rwanda: Aménagement linguistique dans le monde | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140101120624/http://www.axl.cefan.ulaval.ca/afrique/rwanda.htm | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.axl.cefan.ulaval.ca/afrique/rwanda.htm | accessdate = 2012-02-16 | archivedate = 2014-01-01 }}</ref>。20世纪末从乌干达或其他地区涌入的难民<ref name="Université Laval-2010" />及其后代以[[英语|英语]]为主要语言，因此和国内的法语人口间形成了语言上的鸿沟<ref name="Samuelson-Freedman-2010">{{cite journal | last1 = Samuelson | first1 = Beth Lewis | last2 = Freedman | first2 = Sarah Warshauer | year = 2010 | title = Language policy, multilingual education, and power in Rwanda | journal = Language Policy | issn = 1568-4555 | volume = 9 | issue = 3 | pages = 191-215 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130510021728/http://gse.berkeley.edu/sites/default/files/users/sarah-freedman/10samuelson_freedman.pdf | url = http://gse.berkeley.edu/sites/default/files/users/sarah-freedman/10samuelson_freedman.pdf | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | doi = 10.1007/s10993-010-9170-7 | archivedate = 2013-05-10 | deadurl = yes | author =  }}</ref>。[[卢旺达语|卢旺达语]]、[[英语|英语]]和[[法语|法语]]都是该国的官方语言。政府部门多使用卢旺达语，而教学则以英语为主。东非地区[[通用语|通用]]的[[斯瓦希里语|斯瓦希里语]]也是卢旺达人广泛使用的语言，特别是在农村地区<ref name="Samuelson-Freedman-2010" />。此外，生活在寇伯岛（{{lang|en|Nkombo Island}}）上的居民会说一种名为“{{lang|en|Amashi}}”的语言，这种语言和卢旺达语有着密切的联系<ref name="Nakayima-2010">{{cite news | last = Nakayima | first = Lillian | date = 2010-06-23 | title = Nkombo Island's Hope for the Future | work = The New Times | location = Kigali | url = http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14135&a=30186 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131107063730/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14135&a=30186 | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | archivedate = 2013-11-07 }}</ref>。

== 文化 ==
[[File:Rwanda_IntoreDancers.jpg|thumb]]
音乐和舞蹈是卢旺达的仪式、节庆、社交聚会，以及评书弹词活动中的组成部分。最知名的传统舞蹈经过精心编排，包含三大部分：一种是由女性表演的“{{lang|rw|umushagiriro}}”，又名牛舞<ref name="Rwanda Development Gateway">{{cite web | author = Rwanda Development Gateway | title = National Ballet – Urukerereza | archivedate = 2012-10-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121029073443/http://www.rwandagateway.org/spip.php?article211 | url = http://www.rwandagateway.org/spip.php?article211 | accessdate = 2012-10-29 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>；第二种是由男性表演的“{{lang|rw|intore}}”，又名英雄之舞<ref name="Rwanda Development Gateway" />；还有一种是击鼓舞，传统上也是由男性表演，使用的鼓称为{{lang|rw|ingoma}}<ref name="RMCA">{{cite web | author = Royal Museum for Central Africa (RMCA) | title = Ingoma | url = http://music.africamuseum.be/instruments/english/rwanda/ingoma.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130512191221/http://music.africamuseum.be/instruments/english/rwanda/ingoma.html | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archivedate = 2013-05-12 }}</ref>。[[卢旺达国家歌舞团|卢旺达国家歌舞团]]是该国最具知名度的舞蹈团，由总统朱韦纳尔·哈比亚利马纳在1974年设立，经常在国内和国际上进行演出<ref name="Briggs-2004">{{cite news | last = Briggs | first = Jimmy | date = 2004-08 | title = A dance of hope in Rwanda | work = Dance Magazine | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-119951358.html | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | via = HighBeam Research | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140611124157/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-119951358.html | archivedate = 2014-06-11 }}</ref>。音乐传统上是由口头传授，不同社会群体的音乐风格也相应不同。鼓是非常重要的[[乐器|乐器]]，皇家鼓手在国王的宫廷中享有很高的地位<ref name="Adekunle-2007" />{{rp|135-136}}。鼓手也会组团进行演奏，规模通常为7至9人<ref name="Adekunle-2007" />{{rp|139}}。该国的流行音乐也在不断发展，乐风主要受到东非、刚果和[[美国音乐|美国音乐]]的影响。[[嘻哈|嘻哈]]是最受欢迎的曲风，其中融合了[[饶舌|饶舌]]、[[雷格乐|雷格乐]]、[[节奏布鲁斯|节奏布鲁斯]]和[[舞蹈流行音乐|舞蹈流行音乐]]的特点<ref name="Mbabazi-2008">{{cite news | last = Mbabazi | first = Linda | date = 2008-05-11 | title = Hip Hop Dominating Music Industry | work = The New Times | location = Kigali | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222140135/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/views/article_print.php?14178&a=6255&icon=Print | url = http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/views/article_print.php?14178&a=6255&icon=Print | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | df =  }}</ref>。

[[File:Igiseke.jpg|thumb]]
全国各地都会生产传统工艺和美术品，不过其中大部分最初都属实用工具，而非纯粹作为装饰。编织篮和碗尤为普遍<ref name="Adekunle-2007" />{{rp|68-70}}。卢旺达的东南部制造有一种使用牛粪制作，名为“{{lang|en|Imigongo}}”的独特艺术品，其历史可以追溯到该区域尚属吉萨卡（{{lang|en|Gisaka}}）独立王国组成部分的时代。创作使用的牛粪中混有各种颜色的天然土壤，将其涂成隆起的几何形状图案<ref name="Briggs-Booth-2006" />{{rp|243-244}}。其他工艺品包括陶器和木雕<ref name="Briggs-Booth-2006" />{{rp|31}}。传统房屋大多就地取材，大多为圆形或长方泥，使用泥土搭建并配以茅草制成的屋顶。政府已启动计划，使用像波纹铁之类更为现代化的材料取代传统建材<ref name="Ntambara-2009">{{cite news |last=Ntambara |first=Paul |date=2009-12-09 |title=Minister Irked By Big Number of Grass-Thatched Houses |work=The New Times |location=Kigali |url=http://newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14104&a=24347 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2014-04-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202112037/http://newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?i=14104&a=24347 |archivedate=2014-02-02 }}</ref><ref name="Adekunle-2007" />{{rp|75}}。

卢旺达的书面文学历史较短，但从[[诗歌|诗歌]]到[[民俗学|民俗]]在内的多个领域都有着悠久的口述传统，该国的许多道德观念和历史详情都是如此世代传承下来<ref name="King 2007" />{{rp|105}}。已故作家[[亚历克西斯·卡加梅|亚历克西斯·卡加梅]]（{{lang|en|Alexis Kagame}}）是卢旺达最具影响的文学代表人物，他出版了自己对口述传统的研究成果，并创作了大量的诗歌<ref name="Briggs-Booth-2006" />{{rp|29}}。卢旺达大屠杀成为许多文艺作品的素材，如记录目击者证词的记实文学，包括本杰明·赛恩（{{lang|en|Benjamin Sehene}}）在内的新生代作家创作的[[散文|散文]]和[[小说|小说]]。还有多部电影也是以这起惨案为题材，如曾获[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]和[[金球奖|金球奖]]提名的《[[卢旺达饭店|卢旺达饭店]]》<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-12-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131230233519/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/2000-present/77nominees.html | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/2000-present/77nominees.html | title = Nominees & Winners for the 77th Academy Awards | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | publisher = Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hfpa.org/browse/?param=/film/25931 |title=Hotel Rwanda |accessdate=2014-04-18 |publisher=HOLLYWOOD FOREIGN PRESS ASSOCIATION |work=hfpa.org |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220080701/http://www.hfpa.org/browse/?param=%2Ffilm%2F25931 |archivedate=2014-02-20 }}</ref>，《[[与恶魔携手|与恶魔携手]]》（{{lang|en|''Shake Hands with the Devil''}}）、《[[泣血四月|泣血四月]]》和《[[杀戮禁区|杀戮禁区]]》（{{lang|en|''Shooting Dogs''}}）等，其中后两部是在卢旺达实地拍摄，并且还有当年的幸存者参与演出<ref name="Milmo-2006">{{cite news | last = Milmo | first = Cahal | date = 2006-03-29 | title = Flashback to terror: Survivors of Rwandan genocide watch screening of Shooting Dogs | work = The Independent | archivedate = 2014-02-26 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140226214258/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/flashback-to-terror-survivors-of-rwandan-genocide-watch-screening-of-shooting-dogs-471825.html | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | location = London | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/flashback-to-terror-survivors-of-rwandan-genocide-watch-screening-of-shooting-dogs-471825.html }}</ref>。

卢旺达每年有11个国家法定节假日，政府偶尔还会安排其他公众假期<ref name="Embassy of Rwanda in Sudan">{{cite web | author = Embassy of Rwanda in Sudan | title = Sudan and Rwanda public holidays | archivedate = 2012-03-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120313155356/http://sudan.embassy.gov.rw/content/view/42/97/ | deadurl = yes | url = http://sudan.embassy.gov.rw/content/view/42/97/ | accessdate = 2012-03-13 }}</ref>。4月7日是种族灭绝惨案的纪念日，其后的一星期则是官方正式的哀悼周<ref name="Directorate General of Immigration and Emigration">{{cite web | author = Directorate General of Immigration and Emigration, Republic of Rwanda | title = General Information | page = 5 | url = http://migration.gov.rw/IMG/pdf/General_Information.pdf | accessdate = 2012-03-07 | archivedate = 2011-10-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111003095559/http://www.migration.gov.rw/IMG/pdf/General_Information.pdf | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。每年的7月4日是[[解放日|解放日]]，用来庆祝卢旺达爱国阵线战胜胡图族极端分子。每个月的最后一个星期六则是“乌姆干达”（{{lang|rw|''umuganda''}}），是一个旨在提供[[社区服务|社区服务]]的全国性节日，期间的大部分普通服务从早上7点开始，持续到中午12点为止<ref name=Gahindiro-2008>{{cite news | last = Gahindiro | first = John | date = 2008-06-02 | title = Making "Umuganda" More Useful | work = The New Times | location = Kigali | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202112533/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/views/article_print.php?13550&a=6830 | url = http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/views/article_print.php?13550&a=6830 | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | archivedate = 2014-02-02 | df =  }}</ref>。

=== 饮食 ===
卢旺达的饮食主要由当地自给农业生产的[[主食|主食]]制作，如香蕉、大蕉（当地称“{{lang|en|Ibitoke}}）”、[[番薯|番薯]]、豆类、[[木薯|木薯]]等<ref name="Adekunle-2007" />{{rp|81}}。大部分卢旺达人一个月只会吃为数不多的几次肉食<ref name="Adekunle-2007" />{{rp|81}}。[[罗非鱼|罗非鱼]]很受住在湖边或是其他能捕到鱼地区的居民欢迎<ref name="Adekunle-2007" />{{rp|81}}。土豆据称是由德国和比利时[[新帝国主义|殖民者]]引入卢旺达，也很受当地人的欢迎<ref name="Adekunle-2007" />{{rp|13}}。“[[乌伽黎|乌伽黎]]”（{{lang|rw|Ubugari}}，又称{{lang|rw|umutsima}}）是一种用木薯或玉米配水调制成的[[糊|糊]]状食品，东非其他许多国家和地区也会食用<ref name="Auzias-2007">{{cite book | last = Auzias | first = Dominique | year = 2007 | title = Rwanda | location = Paris | publisher = Petit Futé | isbn = 978-2-7469-2037-8 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=TyMs5XGSIzQC | accessdate = 2014-04-18 | page = 74 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200728133619/https://books.google.com/books?id=TyMs5XGSIzQC | archivedate = 2020-07-28 }}</ref>。“{{lang|en|Isombe}}”由捣碎的木薯叶制成，与鱼干一起食用<ref name="Adekunle-2007" />{{rp|13}}。午餐通常是自助餐形式，人称“{{lang|en|mélange}}”（有“混杂堆积”之意），其中包括上文提及的主食，有些还会有肉食<ref name="Briggs-Booth-2006" />{{rp|66}}。如果晚间外出就餐，最受欢迎的食物则是串烧，食材以羊肉最为常见，偶尔也会有[[牛肚|牛肚]]、[[牛肉|牛肉]]和鱼肉<ref name="Briggs-Booth-2006" />{{rp|66}}。农村地区的许多酒吧会有专门销售串烧食品的卖家，他们会照料和屠宰[[山羊|山羊]]，串烧或[[烧烤|烧烤]]羊肉，还会向食客提供烤香蕉一起食用<ref name="Anyango-2010">{{cite news |last=Anyango |first=Gloria I. |date=2010-02-04 |title=The Barbecue Chef who masters his roast |url=http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?a=2784&week=5 |work=The New Times |location=Kigali |accessdate=2014-04-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422184112/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/index.php?a=2784&week=5 |archivedate=2014-04-22 }}</ref>。牛奶，特别是人称“{{lang|en|ikivuguto}}”的发酵酸奶，在全国各地都是很常见的饮料<ref name="Nzabuheraheza-2005">{{cite journal | last = Nzabuheraheza | first = François Dominicus | year = 2005 | title = Milk Production and Hygiene in Rwanda | journal = African Journal of Food, Agriculture, Nutrition and Development (AJFAND) | issn = 1684-5374 | volume = 5 | issue = 2 | url = http://www.ajfand.net/Volume5/No2/commentaryDominicus.html | accessdate = 2014-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140303175423/http://www.ajfand.net/Volume5/No2/commentaryDominicus.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-03-03 }}</ref>。其它饮品包括一种名为“{{lang|rw|urwagwa}}”的传统啤酒，由高粱或香蕉酿制而成，在传统仪式和庆典中很常见<ref name="Adekunle-2007" />{{rp|13}}。卢旺达酿造的商业[[啤酒|啤酒]]则包括普里默斯（{{lang|en|Primus}}）、米齐格（{{lang|en|Mützig}}）和[[阿姆斯特尔啤酒|阿姆斯特尔]]（{{lang|en|Amstel}}）多个品牌<ref name="Auzias-2007" />。

=== 体育 ===
从国际上来看，卢旺达的[[篮球|篮球]]运动员表现最为出色，其国家队已连续四度打入[[非洲篮球锦标赛|非洲篮球锦标赛]]的最后阶段，还曾申办2013年的赛事<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-02-28 | deadurl = yes | location = Kigali | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140228052221/http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/views/article_print.php?14119&a=24038&icon=Print | url = http://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/views/article_print.php?14119&a=24038&icon=Print | title = Rwanda to bid for 2013 FIBA Africa Championship | publisher = The New Times | accessdate = 2014-02-28 }}</ref>，不过最终赢得申办权的是[[科特迪瓦|科特迪瓦]]<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2012-09-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120913030619/http://www.fibaafrica.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1584:afrobasket-2013-organisation-la-cote-divoire-pays-organisateur&catid=27:afrobasket-hommes&Itemid=73&lang=en |url=http://www.fibaafrica.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1584%3Aafrobasket-2013-organisation-la-cote-divoire-pays-organisateur&catid=27%3Aafrobasket-hommes&Itemid=73&lang=en |title=Afrobasket 2013 – Organization : Cote d'Ivoire will host the competition |accessdate=2012-09-13 }}</ref>。

